(186, 80, 'Numerology & Intuitive Reading - Full Numerology & Astrology Birth Chart Reading - 120 Minutes', 'This is a 120 minute virtual Intuitive Numerology reading with a focus on all of your Soul Codes, Fortunate Name number, Triads and a deep reading into your Astrology Birth Chart Numerology codes.\r\n\r\nFocus Areas\r\n○ Detailed explanation of your 3 main Soul Codes along with your 3 secondary Soul Codes\r\n   (Soul, Personality, Essence)\r\n○ Explanation of the Triads your 6 Soul Codes fall under\r\n○ Fortunate / Challenging names - 1 name options, insights into your current names and\r\n   suggestions if any of your names have a “challenging” vibration\r\n○ Astrology Birth Chart Numerology Reading\r\n          ■ Degree codes within birth chart interpretation\r\n          ■ Degree codes cross correlation to Soul Codes\r\n          ■ Discoveries and Observations\r\n          ■ Astrological & planetary/star codes interpretation\r\n○ Intuitive reading based on your 3 main Soul Codes on one area of focus - Career, Money,\r\n   Love, Relationships, Family, Health / Wellbeing\r\n○ Bonus: Detailed report of your three main Soul Codes and a copy of the recorded session', 'Numerology is the study of the vibrational/energetic meanings of numbers. Numbers are a very active and prevalent part of our everyday lives and can bring different meanings and perspectives when looking at numbers as a whole. \r\n\r\nDid you know..\r\n○ Your day of birth (for anything in life not just the day you were born) and your full birthdate are two of your three main Soul Codes? \r\n○ Your birth certificate name also has a numeric value attached to it and is your third main Soul Code?\r\n○ The names you use on your bank accounts, authorized signing name and the name you use on a day-to-day basis has fortunate and \r\n   challenging vibrations?\r\n\r\nLets learn more together what your Soul Codes say about you. Are you aligned to your life\'s purpose and career choices?', NULL, '[\"7\"]', '[\"39\",\"44\"]', '1742511240_copy.png', '2025-03-20 22:54:00', '2025-03-20 22:59:58', 'virtual', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '393', NULL, NULL, 'Thank you for your investment in your Wholeness. Welcome to Revolution9 - a Wholeness Training and Holistic Healing company. \r\n\r\nYour Wholeness Trainer and Psychic Healer, Maria Esposito, will be your Conduit throughout your Psychic Numerology reading. You will be contacted by Maria shortly so you can provide some information to her regarding your expectations, needs and desires for the session. She will also provide you with some information regarding the session and what you can expect.\r\n\r\nWe look forward to connecting to your shortly.\r\n\r\nWith Appreciation,\r\nMaria Esposito, CHt, NLP, TLT\r\nWholeness Trainer, Psychic Healer, Guide\r\nRevolution9 - Wholeness Training & Consulting', NULL, 1, '24 hour', 1, '2 hour', '115', '30 minutes', 'day');

