(42, 46, 'Distance Reiki Session', 'Reiki is energy work that originated in Japan that supports your healing and relaxation journey.\r\n\r\nWe will begin the session over Zoom or phone call by sharing intentions or areas you wish to work on during your session. I will then provide an oracle card pull as this gives new depth, direction and grounding for the time we will share together. Once this is complete, I will invite you to relax into a space that feels comfortable for you and Reiki will be sent to you. Once the 40 minute reiki session is complete we will connect to have a discussion. Lastly, a session overview will be sent to you via email to support your journey moving forward.\r\n\r\nDuration: 60 minutes', NULL, NULL, '[\"1\",\"4\"]', '[\"7\"]', '1742263666.jpg', '2025-03-02 15:39:04', '2025-03-22 02:06:12', 'virtual', '2025-03-02 15:39:04', NULL, 0, NULL, '88.00', NULL, NULL, 'Thank you so much for booking a session—I\'m looking forward to connecting with you. A Zoom link will be sent to you to utilize for the beginning of our session where we will begin with a gentle conversation to learn more about you and your needs as we open this space together.\r\n\r\nAs you prepare, I invite you to hydrate well and create a quiet, calming space where you can fully relax and receive during the Reiki session.\r\n\r\nWith gratitude,\r\n\r\nJanine', NULL, 1, '24 hour', 1, '1 hour', '115', '1 hour', 'month'),
(43, 46, 'Oracle Card Reading', 'Step into a sacred space of insight, clarity, and deep connection. My oracle card sessions are an intuitive and heart-centered experience designed to support you on your journey forward. Each session is a gentle unfolding, offering messages that align with your soul’s path and the energies present in your life.\r\n\r\nUsing oracle cards as a sacred tool, I channel intuitive guidance to help you gain perspective, clarity, and affirmation for the next steps on your path. Whether you seek reassurance, direction, or a deeper understanding of the energies surrounding you, this session will provide a nurturing space to receive wisdom from the universe, your ancestors, and your higher self.\r\n\r\nCome with an open heart and a willingness to receive. Your soul already knows the way—this session is simply a mirror reflecting the guidance that is already within you.', 'Receive intuitive guidance and clarity as you navigate your path forward. My oracle card sessions create a sacred space for deep insight, affirmation, and connection to your inner wisdom. Each card drawn offers messages from the universe, your ancestors, and your higher self—empowering you to move forward with trust and clarity. This is not about predicting the future but about illuminating possibilities and aligning you with your soul’s journey. Come with an open heart and let the wisdom unfold.', NULL, '[\"7\"]', '[\"13\",\"40\",\"61\"]', '1742264720.webp', '2025-03-02 15:39:41', '2025-03-22 02:05:02', 'virtual', '2025-03-02 15:39:41', NULL, 0, NULL, '55.00', NULL, '2 hours', 'Thank you so much for booking a session—I\'m looking forward to connecting with you. A Zoom link will be sent to you to utilize for the beginning of our session where we will begin with a gentle conversation to learn more about you and your needs as we open this space together.\r\n\r\nAs you prepare, I invite you to hydrate well and create a quiet, calming space where you can fully relax and receive during the session.\r\n\r\nWith gratitude,\r\n\r\nJanine', NULL, 1, '24 hour', 1, '45 minutes', '115', '45 minutes', 'minute'),
(44, 46, 'Soulful Meditation Series - 3 Personalized Meditations', 'This offering is designed to support you exactly where you are on your journey. We will begin with a 30-minute one-on-one session to explore what you need most—whether it\'s grounding, clarity, emotional healing, self-love, or manifestation. From there, I will intuitively craft a series of three personalized, pre-recorded meditations (each 15 minutes long) to align with your unique intentions.\r\n\r\nEach meditation will be infused with guided visualization, breathwork, and crystal bowl sound healing to create a deeply immersive experience. You will also receive journal prompts and personalized suggestions to help you integrate the practices into your daily life and deepen your healing journey.', 'This custom experience is designed to support your unique journey. We’ll begin with a 30-minute session to explore what you need most—whether it\'s grounding, clarity, healing, or manifestation. From there, I’ll create three personalized, pre-recorded meditations (15 minutes each), infused with guided visualization, breathwork, and sound healing. You\'ll also receive journal prompts and suggestions to deepen your practice.', NULL, '[\"9\"]', '[\"11\",\"14\",\"15\",\"25\"]', '1742264583.jpg', '2025-03-02 15:40:52', '2025-03-22 02:05:37', 'virtual', '2025-03-02 15:40:52', NULL, 0, NULL, '55.00', '13%', '2 hour', 'Thank you so much for booking a session—I\'m looking forward to connecting with you. A Zoom link will be sent to you to utilize for the beginning of our session where we will begin with a gentle conversation to learn more about you and your needs as we open this space together.\r\n\r\nAs you prepare, I invite you to hydrate well and create a quiet, calming space where you can fully relax and receive during the time we spend together.\r\n\r\nWith gratitude,\r\n\r\nJanine', NULL, 1, '24 hour', 1, '30 minutes', '115', '1 hour', 'minute'),
