(110, 51, '2 x 60-min Hypnosis Sessions [New Client Offer]', 'Are you ready to remove blocks and reprogram new beliefs that will support you to shift the pressure of feeling like you have to have everything all figured out?\r\n\r\nOr perhaps you need some support moving through physical or emotional discomfort, limiting beliefs, or stuckness.\r\n\r\nYour sessions will be completely customized to you whether you are curious to explore or remove a block that you\'ve been having, connect to your inner child, enjoy a relaxing visualization experience, or simply want to further affirm and enhance a goal you\'re working towards!', 'Untangle the subconscious patterns that are keeping you from embodying your dreams. First time clients can purchase a 2 x 60-mins Private Hypnosis Sessions for a special price.', NULL, '[\"4\",\"6\"]', '[\"20\",\"21\"]', '1742433062.jpeg', '2025-03-10 23:32:24', '2025-03-20 01:11:02', 'virtual', '2025-03-10 23:32:24', NULL, 0, NULL, '222', '5', '1', 'Hi there,\r\n\r\nThank you so much for booking a special Hypnosis offer with me as a first time client — I\'m so glad you\'ve taken this step toward exploring new possibilities for yourself. 💛\r\n\r\nUpon purchasing this offer you will book your first 60-minute session. At the end of the first session, we will manually book in your second 60-minute session that is part of this offer.\r\n\r\nHere’s a few things to consider before your session:\r\n\r\n👉 Come as you are — there\'s no need to prepare anything in advance.\r\nBut if you’d like to, you can take a few moments beforehand to reflect on: What’s one thing you’d love to shift or unlock in your life right now? INSERT INTO `offerings` (`id`, `user_id`, `name`, `long_description`, `short_description`, `help`, `categories`, `tags`, `featured_image`, `created_at`, `updated_at`, `offering_type`, `from_date`, `to_date`, `availability`, `availability_type`, `client_price`, `tax_amount`, `scheduling_window`, `email_template`, `intake_form`, `is_cancelle