(126, 24, 'Energetic Virtual House Cleanse', 'Here’s how a Virtual Energetic House Cleanse using the Spirit of the Home might work:\r\n\r\nSteps in the Spirit of the Home Energetic Cleanse:\r\n\r\n1 . Initial Intention Setting and Connection:\r\n\r\nSetting intentions: You begin by setting an intention for the session. There will be back and forth correspondence where the address, date, and time will be discussed for me to energetically  enter your home. Your agreement to the date and time will grant me one time energetic access to your home, for only this time frame.\r\n\r\nEnergetic connection:  I will connect energetically with the \"Spirit\" or soul of your home. This involves tuning into the unique frequency of your space to understand its energetic patterns and needs.\r\n\r\n2. Assessing the Home’s Energy:\r\n\r\nListening to the Home: I will use intuitive methods to communicate with the energy of the home. This could include sensing any energetic imbalances or \"emotional residues\" left by previous occupants, past events, or environmental factors that have influenced the space.\r\n\r\nIdentifying blocks: I will identify areas of the home that might feel stagnant, heavy, or disconnected, such as dark corners, rooms where energy feels blocked, or places with negative emotional associations.\r\n\r\n3. Cleansing and Releasing Negative Energy:\r\n\r\nShamanic Techniques: I will use shamanic rituals to remove unwanted energy. This could involve energy work such as sound healing (e.g., using drums, bells, or singing bowls)  or calling in spiritual helpers to assist in clearing.\r\n\r\nSpirit Communication: I will engage directly with the spirit of the home, asking for guidance on what needs to be released and working to free the space from any lingering negativity, unwanted energies, or attachments.\r\n\r\n4. Restoring and Rebalancing the Energy:\r\n\r\nInfusing positive energy: After clearing, I will guide the process of infusing the space with renewed energy. This may include invoking healing energy, light, and harmony throughout the home to restore balance.\r\n\r\nHarmonizing the flow: The goal is to create an energetic flow where all areas of the home feel aligned, open, and peaceful. The energy should support the well-being of those who live there, as well as welcome new, positive experiences.\r\n\r\n5. Protection and Energizing the Space (if needed):\r\n\r\nSpiritual Protection: I will likely use protective techniques to shield the home from future negativity. This might involve placing energetic boundaries around the home, calling in protective spirits, or using sacred symbols or crystals to keep the space energetically safeguarded.\r\n\r\nOngoing Activation: Sometimes, I might recommend specific practices (e.g., placing particular objects, crystals, or creating an altar) that help maintain the space’s high energetic vibration. You may also be encouraged to use affirmations or prayers to reinforce the connection with the Spirit of the Home.\r\n\r\n6. Follow-Up and Guidance:\r\n\r\nFeedback on the Home’s Spirit: You will receive feedback in the form of a youtube video sent via a link (so that you can refer to it as many times as needed) on how the session went, including messages from the home’s spirit or any additional guidance on how to keep the energy clear and positive.\r\n\r\nLong-Term Support: I may provide suggestions for maintaining the clean energy in the home, such as regular energetic upkeep, mindful living practices, and fostering a positive atmosphere.\r\n\r\nBenefits of a \"Spirit of the Home\" Energetic Cleanse:\r\n\r\n- Restoring harmony: It helps create a space where the energy feels grounded, peaceful, and balanced, promoting wellness for all who live there.\r\n- Personalized attention: Each home has its own unique energetic signature, and this approach tailors the cleansing process to the specific needs and spirit of your space.\r\n- Healing emotional wounds: The cleanse can help clear emotional or traumatic imprints left in the space, contributing to healing for both the home and the individuals who inhabit it.\r\n\r\nThis type of session, combining spiritual and shamanic practices, aims not just to \"cleanse\" but to align your space with its higher purpose, helping to release stagnant energy and inviting in positive, life-affirming energies.', 'A Virtual Energetic House Cleanse using the Spirit of the Home focuses on connecting with the unique energy of your space to clear negative or stagnant energies and restore balance. Through shamanic practices, intuitive assessments, and energy work, the session removes blockages, infuses positive energy, and harmonizes the flow within the home. The cleanse also involves spiritual protection and guidance for maintaining a peaceful, high-vibration environment. Tailored to the specific needs of your space, this process creates a harmonious atmosphere that supports well-being and healing.', NULL, '[\"4\",\"6\",\"7\"]', '[\"33\",\"34\",\"35\",\"37\"]', '1742396877.jpg', '2025-03-14 19:36:43', '2025-03-19 16:10:23', 'virtual', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '175', NULL, '48', NULL, NULL, 1, '48 hour', 1, '1 hour', '115', '15 minutes', 'hour'),
