(128, 26, 'Tarot-Inspired Creativity Coaching for Writers & Bloggers', 'Feeling stuck in your writing? Experiencing creative blocks or having no clue what to write next? My Tarot-Inspired Creativity Coaching Session will allow you to tap into your intuition, break through mental blocks, and generate fresh ideas for your writing projects.\r\n\r\nWhat You\'ll Receive in This Session:\r\n\r\n✨ Personalized Tarot Reading – Explore your creative process and uncover inner inspiration.\r\n✨ Writer\'s Block Be Gone – Use tarot as a brainstorming tool to break through blockages.\r\n✨ Blog & Content Strategy – Gain insight into planning blog posts, narrative, and theme ideas.\r\n✨ Intuitive Writing Prompts – Get custom tarot-based prompts tailored to your niche.\r\n✨ Writing Practice Tips – Discover how to incorporate tarot with structured writing styles for effortless creativity.\r\n\r\nWho is this for?\r\n\r\n✔ Writers, bloggers, and creatives seeking fresh inspiration\r\n✔ Content creators and writers looking for new story ideas\r\n✔ Anyone experiencing writer\'s block or idea generation\r\n\r\n How It Works:\r\n\r\n1️⃣  60-minute Zoom call or pre-recorded video reading\r\n2️⃣ Discussion of your creative goals and obstacles\r\n3️⃣ A custom tarot spread to uncover information and inspiration\r\n4️⃣ Takeaway action steps, including writing prompts and content ideas\r\n\r\nReady to unleash your creativity? Book your session today!', 'Feeling stuck in your writing? This session uses tarot as a creative tool to spark inspiration, break through writer’s block, and generate fresh blog and content ideas. You\'ll receive a personalized tarot reading, intuitive writing prompts, and practical strategies to plan and structure your work. Whether you need help brainstorming or overcoming creative blocks, this session will guide you toward effortless creativity. Book now to unlock your writing flow!', NULL, '[\"10\"]', '[\"12\",\"28\",\"46\"]', '1742150512.jpg', '2025-03-16 18:41:52', '2