(129, 26, 'Tarot Coaching for Social Media, SEO & Marketing', 'Are you having trouble creating engaging content, catching your dream audience\'s attention, or implementing an effective marketing strategy? This special coaching session blends tarot knowledge with social media, SEO, and marketing tactics to help you create content that speaks.\r\n\r\nWhat You\'ll Be Learning in This Session:\r\n\r\n✨ Personalized Tarot Reading – Gain information about your brand message, content concepts, and audience needs.\r\n✨ Social Media Content Planning – Develop fresh post ideas, storytelling possibilities, and engagement strategies.\r\n✨ SEO-Optimized Content Guidance – Discover how to link tarot-inspired insights with keyword strategies for better visibility.\r\n✨ Brand Alignment & Authenticity – Allow your content to be your genuine voice and speak directly to your people on a deeper level.\r\n✨ Marketing Strategy & Engagement Tips – Discover strategies to engage and keep followers through intentional, intuitive marketing.\r\n\r\nWho is it for?\r\n\r\n✔ Entrepreneurs, coaches, and creatives looking for off-the-beaten-path ideas for content\r\n✔ Social media managers looking for more depth-driven engagement strategies\r\n✔ Marketers in need of having their marketing efforts connected to purpose\r\n✔ Anyone stuck on ideas for creating, sustaining, and getting noticed through content\r\n\r\nHow It Works:\r\n\r\n1️⃣  60-minute Zoom session or pre-recorded video read-through\r\n2️⃣ Discovery of your content, audience, and marketing challenges\r\n3️⃣ A customized tarot spread for marketing and social media guidance\r\n4️⃣ Practical insights, including content ideas and SEO advice\r\n\r\nWant to transform your social media and marketing using tarot? Schedule an appointment today and bring creativity, strategy, and alignment into your content!', 'Struggling with content creation, audience engagement, or marketing strategy? This session combines tarot insights with social media and SEO strategies to help you generate fresh content ideas, refine your brand messaging, and align your marketing with your authentic voice. You\'ll uncover content themes, engagement strategies, and SEO-friendly ideas through a personalized tarot reading to boost visibility and connection. Book now to create aligned, impactful content with intuitive guidance!', NULL, '[\"10\"]', '[\"12\",\"47\"]', '1742150856.jpg', '2025-03-16 18:47:36', '2025-03-16 18:47:36', 'virtual', NULL, NULL, 1, 'every_day', '150', NULL, '24 hour', NULL, NULL, 1, '24 hour', 1, '1 hour', '115', '15 minutes', NULL),
(130, 54, 'First Steam Ritual Session', 'Step into a soft, sacred space where you can slow down and reconnect with yourself. This session is an invitation to explore the ritual of yoni steaming with intention and support. Before your session, you’ll complete an intake so I can craft an herbal blend aligned with your body’s needs and desires. When you arrive, we’ll settle into a welcoming circle, sip tea, pull oracle cards and gently open the ritual together. There is space here—space to share, to breathe, to listen to your body. As you move into your steam, you’ll be fully held in the warmth of this practice. Afterward, you’ll have time to rest in a cozy bed area, journal or simply be with yourself. When you feel ready, we’ll close the session in circle, offering time for reflection and integration. This is more than just a steam—it’s a moment to return to yourself, to honor your body and to embrace your wholeness.', 'A nurturing, in-person experience to explore yoni steaming in a sacred space. We’ll open with tea, oracle cards, and intention setting before your guided steam, followed by time for rest, reflection, and integration.', NULL, '[\"5\"]', '[\"4\",\"5\",\"6\"]', '1742165814.jfif', '2025-03-16 19:39:37', '2025-03-17 03:28:59', 'in-person', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '120', NULL, NULL, 'Thank you for booking a First Steam Ritual Session! I’m so honored to support you on this journey of connecting with your womb and integrating steaming into your self-care practice.', 'https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdMTZZxSz2a0eX25jkj0rZE6MJifKuR0W2DIyNkaID1gTsaVA/viewform?usp=sharing', 1, '48 hour', 0, '1 hour', '752', '30 minutes', NULL),
(131, 54, 'The Womb Room | Aries', 'Join us for this month’s Womb Room as we gather to ignite our inner fire and connect with the passionate energy of Aries season. This workshop is for women who want to reconnect with their creative power, awaken their inner spark, and feel supported by a community of like-minded sisters.\r\n\r\nThrough guided meditation, ritual, and sharing, we’ll honor the flame of creation within us—tapping into courage, passion, and the bold energy of new beginnings. Whether you’re seeking inspiration, renewal, or deeper connection to your womb and feminine power, this space is for you.\r\n\r\nCome as you are and leave feeling grounded, inspired, and ready to carry your inner fire into the world.', 'Join me in The Womb Room as we gather to ignite our inner fire and connect with the passionate energy of Aries season. Through guided meditation, ritual, and heartfelt sharing, we’ll awaken the spark of life within our womb space—honoring our creative power, courage, and the bold beginnings that arise from our deepest essence. Light your flame, embody your passion, and feel supported by the collective fire of sisterhood.', NULL, '[\"5\"]', '[\"6\",\"11\",\"15\",\"25\",\"53\"]', '1742165842.PNG', '2025-03-16 22:36:57', '2025-03-17 03:30:47', 'virtual', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 0, '48 hour', 0, NULL, '115', NULL, NULL),
(132, 54, 'Deepening the Ritual Session', 'As you continue deepening your relationship with yoni steaming, this session offers a space to nurture your practice, refine your rituals and realign with your intentions. Whether you’re integrating new tools, shifting your focus or simply seeking a moment of stillness, this experience will meet you where you are. We’ll begin in circle, just as before—tea, oracle cards and reflection on what’s present for you. With your personalized herbal blend prepared, you’ll enter your steam, letting the warmth and plant medicine support your journey. Afterward, you’ll have space to rest, breathe, journal or integrate however feels best. As we close the session together, we’ll honor the shifts unfolding within you and the wisdom your body continues to reveal.', 'For those continuing their steaming journey, this session refines your ritual and deepens your connection. With space for reflection, a personalized herbal blend, and gentle integration, this is a moment to honor your evolving practice.', NULL, '[\"5\"]', '[\"4\",\"5\",\"6\"]', '1742166157.png', '2025-03-16 23:02:18', '2025-03-17 03:33:14', 'in-person', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '90', NULL, '2 hour', 'Thank you for booking a Deepening the Ritual Session! I’m so honored to support you on this journey of connecting with your womb and continuing to add steaming into your self-care practice.\r\nIf anything has changed since our last session, please fill in a new intake form. This will help me understand your cycle, concerns, goals and any sensitivities so I can provide the best guidance for you.', 'https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSdMTZZxSz2a0eX25jkj0rZE6MJifKuR0W2DIyNkaID1gTsaVA/viewform?usp=sharing', 1, '48 hour', 1, '1 hour', '752', '30 minutes', NULL),
(133, 71, '30 Minute Tarot Reading - In-Person in Orangeville ON', 'In-Person Reading - A tarot reading offers a unique opportunity for insight. Whether you\'re seeking clarity on a specific issue, or looking for a general guidance, a tarot reading provides intuitive wisdom to help you make informed decisions and embrace personal growth. \r\n\r\nI was given my first tarot deck when I was thirteen, over 35 years ago, which started my lifelong journey with tarot. Over time, tarot has become a tool for guidance, and clarity, offering insight for both myself and others to navigate the challenges and mysteries of life.\r\n\r\nAll in person offerings take place at Healing Moon in Orangeville Ontario, Canada.', '30 minute tarot reading in Orangeville ON to address 1-2 questions.', NULL, '[\"7\"]', '[\"12\",\"61\",\"62\"]', '1742221369_copy.jpg', '2025-03-17 14:22:49', '2025-03-17 16:13:16', 'in-person', '2025-03-02 17:46:49', NULL, 0, NULL, '75', NULL, '2 hour', NULL, NULL, 1, '24 hour', 1, '30 minutes', '115', '30 minutes', NULL),
