(135, 71, '60 minute Reiki Session - In-Person in Orangeville ON', 'In-Person Session - Reiki is a healing practice that can help bring balance to your mind, body, and spirit. Through gentle, energy work, it helps restore alignment where you need it most.  Whether you\'re dealing with physical discomfort, emotional blockages, or just want to find more peace in your life, Reiki works with your unique needs to support your overall wellness.', '60 minute in-person reiki session', NULL, '[\"1\",\"4\",\"7\"]', '[\"7\",\"33\"]', '1742222300_copy.jpg', '2025-03-17 14:38:20', '2025-03-17 15:13:24', 'in-person', '2025-03-02 17:45:20', NULL, 0, NULL, '50', NULL, '2 hour', NULL, NULL, 1, '24 hour', 1, '30 minutes', '115', '30 minutes', NULL),
(136, 71, 'Aromatherapy Session - In-Person in Orangeville ON', 'In-Person Session - Are you struggling with pain, skin issues, sleep irregularities, hormonal changes or menopause? Essential oils and aromatherapy can help support you and your health challenges.\r\n\r\nFIRST APPOINTMENT: During your first aromatherapy session, we start with your intake form to understand your health history, current concerns, and goals. I believe in a holistic approach in order to completely understand where you currently are with your health.\r\n\r\nBETWEEN APPOINTMENTS: I will create a blend of essential oils chosen to address your specific health needs. This blend can be created into a lotion, oil or inhaler depending on your preference.\r\n\r\nSECOND APPOINTMENT: Your aromatherapy blend will be ready approximately one week after your first appointment. This appointment will only be about 15-20 minutes to address any questions you may have as well go over any application instructions.\r\n\r\nAll essential oils used in my sessions are sourced from reputable suppliers and are tested for quality and pureness. I follow strict guidelines for dilution and application to ensure safe and effective use. If you have allergies, sensitivities, or specific medical conditions, I will take extra care to avoid any contraindications and ensure a safe experience.  \r\n\r\n$155 - Includes initial consultation, follow-up appointment and aromatherapy product\r\n\r\nAll in person offerings take place at Healing Moon in Orangeville Ontario, Canada.\r\n\r\nMeghan is a certified aromatherapist with the Canadian Federation of Aromatherapy.', 'Aromatherapy and essential oils are used to promote physical and emotional well-being', NULL, '[\"5\",\"11\"]', '[\"17\",\"49\",\"50\",\"52\",\"54\",\"55\",\"56\",\"57\",\"58\"]', '1742222986.jpg', '2025-03-17 14:49:46', '2025-03-17 15:11:50', 'in-person', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '155', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, '24 hour', 1, '1 hour', '1019', '1 hour', NULL),
