(146, 80, 'Time Line Therapy® - Introduction (1st session) - 3 Hours', 'This 3 hour Introduction session is for someone who hasn\'t had prior Time Line Therapy® experience. During this session we will establish your Time Line, go through a \"practice run\" then going through the intervention session. The areas of focus for this session are as follows.\r\n\r\nFocus Area: \r\n○ Major negative emotions: Anger, Sadness, Fear, Hurt, Guilt, Rage (if required)\r\n○ Limiting Decisions', 'This is a 3 Hour Introduction to Time Line Therapy®. You have a choice of this being an in-person or virtual session. Session are available the following days and times based on availability.\r\nMonday: 10am - 5pm - Virtual\r\nTuesday: 11am - 5pm - In-Person\r\nWednesday: 2pm - 6pm - Virtual\r\nFriday: 10am - 5pm - Virtual\r\nSaturday: Virtual upon request', NULL, '[\"6\"]', '[\"69\"]', '1742256280.png', '2025-03-18 00:04:40', '2025-03-18 00:22:36', NULL, NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '396', NULL, '1 hour', 'Thank you for your investment in your Wholeness. Welcome to Revolution9 - a Wholeness Training and Holistic Healing company. \r\n\r\nYour Wholeness Trainer and Psychic Healer, Maria Esposito, will be your Conduit throughout your Introduction to Time Line Therapy® journey. \r\n\r\nYou will be contacted by Maria shortly so you can provide some information to her regarding your expectations, needs and desires for the session. She will also provide you with some information regarding the session and what you can expect.\r\n\r\nWe look forward to connecting to your shortly.\r\n\r\nWith Appreciation,\r\nMaria Esposito, CHt, NLP, TLT\r\nWholeness Trainer, Psychic Healer, Guide\r\nRevolution9 - Wholeness Training & Consulting', NULL, 1, '24 hour', 1, NULL, '115', '30 minutes', NULL),
