(167, 15, 'In-Person Group Somatic Wellness Session', 'This workshop is a great way to begin and end a project, event, or meeting.  It settles folks in, makes way for grounding,  and allows for embodied presence where all senses are engaged and perspectives are widened.  It\'s a beautiful way for folks to release pent up energy and ease into openings and possibilities for what\'s ahead.  Minimum of 5 people and maximum of 12 per group.  If more or less, please contact Jothi to customize this offering for your needs.', 'Jothi will take you and your class, team, event, staff on a journey with Somatic movement and touch getting folks out of their head and into their feeling body.  They will leave feeling more attuned to what they need, relaxed and clear headed.', NULL, '[\"7\",\"9\"]', '[\"11\",\"14\",\"22\",\"23\",\"24\"]', '1742346279_copy.jpg', '2025-03-19 01:04:39', '2025-03-19 01:05:25', 'in-person', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '300', '13%', NULL, 'Thank you for contacting me, I will be in touch with a confirmation email shortly!', NULL, 1, '48 hour', 1, '1 hour', '115', '1 hour', 'day'),
(168, 24, 'Connect with Your Spirit Guide, Deity, or Ancestors - 1 Hour', 'Discover the Sacred Energies Guiding Your Path\r\n\r\nThis transformative session is a sacred opportunity to establish a direct connection with the spiritual beings who guide and support you. Whether you\'re seeking to meet your spirit guide, form a deeper relationship with a deity, or understand the messages of your ancestors, this experience will help you bridge the gap between the physical and spiritual realms.\r\n\r\nWhat to Expect\r\n\r\n1. Sacred Space Creation\r\nBefore the session starts, I will create sacred space—energetically and physically. Using elements such as incense, candles, or crystals, including protection and the calling in the spiritual energies aligned with your highest good.\r\n\r\n2.Setting Intentions\r\nWe’ll discuss your intentions and focus. Whether you’re seeking to meet a spirit guide, connect with a deity, or understand ancestral guidance, this step helps clarify your goals and ensures the session is tailored to your needs. You’ll also receive tips on grounding and opening your energy to the experience.\r\n\r\n\r\n3. Guided Meditation or Journey\r\nThrough a carefully guided meditation or Shamanic journey, you’ll enter a relaxed, receptive state. This immersive process uses visualization, sound, and intention to guide you to the spiritual plane where your guide, deity, or ancestors await.\r\n\r\n4. Meeting Your Spiritual Allies\r\nOnce in this sacred space, you’ll have the opportunity to meet and connect with the spiritual presence aligned with your current journey. Whether it’s a spirit guide offering wisdom, a deity extending their energy, or an ancestor sharing their love and lessons, this experience is deeply personal and unique.\r\n\r\n5. Receiving Messages\r\nDuring this connection, you may receive messages, images, emotions, or symbols. I’ll help interpret and validate these insights, ensuring they align with your intentions and provide practical guidance for your path.\r\n\r\n6. Integration and Grounding\r\nAfter the journey, we’ll focus on grounding back into the present moment, reflecting on your experience, and integrating the wisdom gained. You’ll receive tips on how to continue nurturing this connection through rituals, offerings, journaling, or meditation practices.\r\n\r\n7. Personalized Follow-Up\r\nWe’ll conclude with a brief discussion of how to maintain and strengthen your bond with your spiritual allies. This includes practices and tools tailored to your unique spiritual path, ensuring ongoing support beyond the session.\r\n\r\n\r\nWho It’s For:\r\nThis session is perfect for those feeling called to connect with unseen guides, deepen their spiritual practice, or seek clarity and support from higher realms. No prior experience is required; come as you are, open to receiving.\r\n\r\nStep into a space of empowerment and wonder. Your spiritual allies are ready to walk this journey with you—let’s meet them together.', 'Discover the Sacred Energies Guiding Your Path\r\n\r\nThis transformative session is a sacred opportunity to establish a direct connection with the spiritual beings who guide and support you. Whether you\'re seeking to meet your spirit guide, form a deeper relationship with a deity, or understand the messages of your ancestors, this experience will help you bridge the gap between the physical and spiritual realms.', NULL, '[\"6\",\"7\"]', '[\"25\",\"35\",\"37\",\"61\"]', '1742397074.jpg', '2025-03-19 15:11:14', '2025-03-19 15:11:14', 'virtual', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '150', NULL, '48', NULL, NULL, 1, '24 hour', 0, '1 hour', '115', '15 minutes', 'hour'),
(169, 24, 'Exploring Spirituality, Shamanism, and Witchcraft: A 3-Hour Transformational Chat', 'Join me for an immersive, heart-centered discussion that dives deep into the realms of spirituality, Shamanism, and witchcraft. This interactive session is designed to explore your unique spiritual path, answer questions, and share wisdom to empower and inspire your journey. \r\n\r\nWhat We Can Cover:\r\n\r\nUnderstanding Your Path:\r\n- How to align with your spiritual purpose and uncover your innate gifts.\r\n- Ways to connect with your higher self, spirit guides, and the energies around you.\r\n\r\nShamanic Practices:\r\n- An introduction to Shamanic journeying and working with spirit allies.\r\n- The role of ancestors, and natural elements in spiritual growth.\r\n\r\nMagick and Witchcraft:\r\n- Foundations of spellwork, ritual crafting, and working with lunar and elemental energies.\r\n- Exploring tools like altars, herbs, and sacred objects to enhance your practice.\r\n\r\nQ&amp;A and Personal Insights:\r\n- A chance to ask questions about your spiritual journey and receive intuitive insights.\r\n- Discuss how to integrate spirituality into your daily life with authenticity and ease.\r\n\r\nWhat to Expect:\r\n\r\n- A safe and sacred space where all questions and perspectives are welcomed.\r\n- Insightful conversation tailored to your interests and needs.\r\n- Practical tools and guidance to help you deepen your connection to spirit.\r\n- Worksheets and resources as required.\r\n\r\nWhether you\'re a beginner curious about these topics or an experienced practitioner looking to expand your knowledge, this chat offers a unique opportunity for connection, discovery, and empowerment.', 'Join me for an immersive, heart-centered discussion that dives deep into the realms of spirituality, Shamanism, and witchcraft. This interactive session is designed to explore your unique spiritual path, answer questions, and share wisdom to empower and inspire your journey.', NULL, '[\"4\",\"6\",\"7\"]', '[\"35\",\"37\",\"38\",\"61\"]', '1742397641.jpg', '2025-03-19 15:20:41', '2025-03-19 15:38:41', 'virtual', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '450', NULL, '48', 'Thank you for your interest in this immersive, heart-centered discussion on spirituality, Shamanism, and witchcraft. I\'m thrilled to welcome you into this sacred space where we’ll explore your unique spiritual path and deepen your connection to the unseen realms.\r\n\r\nWhat You Can Expect:\r\n✔️ Personalized insights into your spiritual journey\r\n✔️ An introduction to Shamanic practices and spirit allies\r\n✔️ Magickal foundations, spellwork, and ritual crafting\r\n✔️ A supportive space for your questions and exploration\r\n✔️ Practical tools and guidance to integrate spirituality into daily life\r\n\r\nThis is more than just a conversation—it\'s a transformative experience designed to inspire and empower you. I\'ll be in touch soon with more details on next steps and scheduling. If you have any questions in the meantime, feel free to reach out.\r\n\r\nLooking forward to this journey together!', 'https://form.jotform.com/243327995100254', 1, '24 hour', 1, NULL, '115', '15 minutes', 'hour'),
(170, 24, '6-Month Mentorship: Unlocking Your Spiritual Path', 'Explore Your Inner Power Through Spirituality, Shamanism, and Witchcraft\r\n\r\nStep into a sacred container for personal transformation with this student-taught mentorship program. Over six months, we will journey together through Shamanic practices, spiritual empowerment, and magickal exploration. Inspired by ancient wisdom and intuitive guidance, this program is designed to help you embody your highest self and align with your unique spiritual gifts. This is 100% catered to you and will only cover topics you wish to learn or expand upon.\r\n\r\nWhat You Can Experience:\r\n\r\n- Shamanic Teachings: Learn to connect with spirit guides, ancestors, and elemental energies.\r\n- Witchcraft Practices: Craft rituals and spells that reflect your intentions and inner wisdom.\r\n- Healing and Activation: Clear blockages, balance chakras, and awaken your innate gifts.\r\n- Spiritual Leadership: Develop confidence in guiding others and anchoring sacred spaces.\r\n\r\nProgram Highlights\r\nThis 6-month mentorship program is a deep dive into spirituality, Shamanism, and witchcraft. Each highlight that you can chose from is designed to empower your journey, drawing from ancient traditions and intuitive wisdom. It may include but not limited to:\r\n\r\nSacred Space Creation\r\n- Learn to craft personal rituals that clear, protect, and energize your space.\r\n- Explore techniques for setting intentions and anchoring energy in your surroundings.\r\n- Develop a deeper connection to the elements, using Earth, Air, Fire, Water, and Spirit to charge your sacred spaces.\r\n\r\nJourneying Techniques\r\n- Master the art of Shamanic journeying to access higher realms and gain insights from spirit guides, ancestors, and the natural world.\r\n- Engage with your personal spirit allies, including animals, totems, and archetypal energies.\r\n- Learn to navigate both light and shadow aspects of the spiritual landscape with confidence and protection.\r\n\r\nHealing and Activation Practices\r\n- Unlock the tools to clear energetic blockages and bring balance to yourself and others.\r\n- Dive into chakra alignment and energy healing techniques to enhance your spiritual well-being.\r\n- Receive activations that awaken dormant spiritual gifts, helping you step into your power.\r\n\r\nSpiritual Empowerment\r\n- Develop a personal practice that reflects your unique spiritual path.\r\n- Learn to integrate Shamanic and witchcraft tools into your daily life, bringing alignment and purpose to all you do.\r\n\r\nRitual and Spell crafting\r\n- Discover the art of designing rituals that align with your intentions and spiritual needs.\r\n- Work with lunar phases, elemental energies, and magickal correspondences to manifest your goals.\r\n- Create spells and tools that are uniquely attuned to your personal journey.\r\n\r\nShadow Work and Integration\r\n- Explore techniques for understanding and integrating the shadow aspects of your psyche.\r\n- Learn how shadow work can serve as a powerful tool for healing, growth, and self-discovery.\r\n-  Transform fears and blockages into sources of wisdom and strength.\r\n\r\nPersonalized Mentorship\r\n- Each session is tailored to your goals, challenges, and unique spiritual gifts.\r\n- Receive direct guidance and intuitive insights to help you navigate your journey.\r\n- Build a lasting foundation for growth, self-awareness, and spiritual alignment.\r\n\r\nYour Mentorship Includes:\r\n- One-on-one semi-monthly sessions for deep exploration lasting an hour each.\r\n- Worksheets, tools, resource, and personal meditations to help you with your growth.\r\n- A safe, welcoming space to learn, practice, and evolve.\r\n- Tools, teachings, and encouragement to embody your spiritual truth.\r\n\r\nWho This Is For:\r\nThis mentorship is perfect for anyone looking to embrace Shamanic and magickal practices, connect with spirit, and live a spiritually aligned life. Whether you’re just beginning or seeking deeper insights, this journey will empower you to step fully into your divine potential.', 'Explore Your Inner Power Through Spirituality, Shamanism, and Witchcraft\r\n\r\nStep into a sacred container for personal transformation with this student-taught mentorship program. Over six months, we will journey together through Shamanic practices, spiritual empowerment, and magickal exploration. Inspired by ancient wisdom and intuitive guidance, this program is designed to help you embody your highest self and align with your unique spiritual gifts. This is 100% catered to you and will only cover topics you wish to learn or expand upon.', NULL, '[\"4\",\"6\",\"7\"]', '[\"11\",\"35\",\"37\",\"38\",\"61\"]', '1742399016.jpeg', '2025-03-19 15:43:36', '2025-03-19 16:09:53', 'virtual', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '2000', NULL, '48', 'Thank you for your interest in this transformative 6-month mentorship program! I’m honored that you feel called to embark on this journey into spirituality, Shamanism, and witchcraft.\r\n\r\nYour application is currently under review, and I’ll be in touch soon with the next steps. If approved, you’ll have the opportunity to:\r\n\r\n🌿 Connect with Spirit – Work with guides, ancestors, and elemental energies\r\n🕯 Deepen Your Practice – Craft rituals, spells, and sacred spaces\r\n💫 Heal & Activate – Clear blockages, balance chakras, and awaken your gifts\r\n🔥 Step into Your Power – Integrate shadow work and spiritual leadership\r\n\r\nI appreciate your patience as I carefully review each application to ensure the best possible experience for every participant. If you have any questions in the meantime or would like to share more about your intentions for this mentorship, feel free to reach out.\r\n\r\nLooking forward to connecting soon!', 'https://form.jotform.com/243326889984073', 1, '24 hour', 1, '2 hour', '115', '15 minutes', 'hour'),
(171, 24, 'The Psychic Reading on Healing That Needs to Be Done - 30 Minutes', 'The Psychic Reading on Healing That Needs to Be Done session is a focused and intuitive experience designed to uncover areas in your life that require healing. Whether it\'s emotional wounds, physical imbalances, spiritual disconnect, or energetic blockages, this session allows you to gain clarity on the specific healing work that needs to be addressed in order to move forward in a balanced, healthy, and empowered way. By channeling insights from your higher self, spirit guides, or loved ones, we will explore what is holding you back, and how to heal and release these obstacles in alignment with your soul\'s highest good.\r\n\r\nWhat to Expect:\r\nPsychic Reading on Healing Areas: Using my intuitive abilities, I will focus on the healing that needs to be done in your life. This may involve exploring different aspects such as:\r\n\r\nEmotional Healing: Identifying past emotional wounds, trauma, grief, or unresolved feelings that need attention and healing.\r\nPhysical Healing: Pinpointing areas of physical discomfort or illness that may have an emotional or spiritual cause.\r\nSpiritual Healing: Exploring areas where you may feel disconnected from your higher self, purpose, or the divine. This could include feelings of spiritual stagnation, a lack of direction, or disconnection from your intuition.\r\nEnergetic Blockages: Assessing your energy field (aura) for any blockages or stagnant energy that may be preventing the flow of positive energy and manifesting as challenges in your life.\r\n\r\nDuring this portion, you may receive information such as:\r\n\r\nThe root cause of your healing needs, whether from past experiences, ancestral patterns, or karmic imprints.\r\nSpecific emotions or beliefs that are keeping you stuck.\r\nInsights into how certain relationships or life situations are contributing to your current state of imbalance.\r\n\r\nHealing Recommendations &amp; Guidance: After identifying the areas of healing that need attention, I will provide detailed guidance on how to address them. This could include:\r\n\r\nReleasing Negative Patterns: Techniques or advice on releasing limiting beliefs, past traumas, or negative emotions that are holding you back from healing.\r\nHealing Tools and Practices: Suggestions for specific healing practices that resonate with you, such as meditation, energy healing, chakra balancing, or journaling.\r\nSelf-Care Practices: Personalized recommendations on how to nurture yourself physically, emotionally, and spiritually to support your healing journey. This may include the use of affirmations, visualization techniques, or practices to create healthier boundaries.\r\nSpiritual &amp; Energy Healing: Insights on whether you need specific energetic work such as chakra healing, aura cleansing, or working with healing crystals or sacred symbols.\r\nEnergy Healing &amp; Cleansing (if applicable): Depending on the psychic reading, there may be an opportunity for me to perform an energy healing or cleansing during the session. This may include:\r\n\r\nAura Cleansing: Clearing any negative or stagnant energy from your aura and energy field.\r\nChakra Healing: Restoring balance to your chakras, helping to clear any blockages and align your energy centers.\r\nCord Cutting: Releasing any unhealthy energetic attachments or cords that may be contributing to your emotional pain or spiritual disconnection.\r\nReiki or Healing Energy Channeling: Sending healing energy to areas of your life that need transformation and balance.\r\nIntegration &amp; Healing Plan: After the psychic insights and healing work, we will create an integration plan. This will help you move forward in your healing process with clear steps and actionable items. I will guide you on how to incorporate the healing messages and practices into your daily life to ensure lasting transformation.\r\n\r\nBenefits of the Psychic Reading on Healing That Needs to Be Done:\r\n\r\nClarity on Healing Needs: Gain insight into which areas of your life require immediate healing and attention, whether emotional, physical, spiritual, or energetic.\r\nEmotional Release: Let go of past traumas, grief, and limiting beliefs that are preventing you from living a fully empowered life.\r\nSpiritual Growth: Reconnect with your spiritual purpose and higher self, clearing any obstacles preventing you from stepping into your full potential.\r\nEmpowerment: Receive clear guidance on how to take charge of your own healing and make positive changes in your life.\r\nPersonalized Healing Plan: Walk away with a practical plan for your healing journey, tailored to your unique needs.\r\n\r\nWho Can Benefit:\r\n\r\nThis session is ideal for anyone who feels stuck, overwhelmed, or disconnected from their true self and purpose. If you are experiencing emotional distress, physical discomfort, spiritual confusion, or simply need clarity on the healing you need to do, this session can provide the insights and guidance you are seeking. It is especially helpful for:\r\n\r\nIndividuals seeking emotional healing or wanting to process grief, trauma, or past pain.\r\nPeople who are feeling spiritually lost or disconnected.\r\nThose experiencing physical symptoms that may have an energetic or emotional cause.\r\nAnyone looking to deepen their self-awareness and empower their healing process.\r\n\r\nThe Psychic Reading on Healing That Needs to Be Done session offers you the clarity, guidance, and healing you need to release what no longer serves you and step into a new chapter of growth, empowerment, and wholeness. Let this session be a catalyst for deep transformation and healing.', 'The Psychic Reading on Healing That Needs to Be Done session is a focused and intuitive experience designed to uncover areas in your life that require healing. Whether it\'s emotional wounds, physical imbalances, spiritual disconnect, or energetic blockages, this session allows you to gain clarity on the specific healing work that needs to be addressed in order to move forward in a balanced, healthy, and empowered way. By channeling insights from your higher self, spirit guides, or loved ones, we will explore what is holding you back, and how to heal and release these obstacles in alignment with your soul\'s highest good.', NULL, '[\"4\",\"6\",\"7\"]', '[\"13\",\"35\",\"37\",\"39\",\"40\",\"61\"]', '1742400111.jpg', '2025-03-19 16:01:51', '2025-03-19 16:09:43', 'virtual', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '75', NULL, '48', NULL, NULL, 1, '24 hour', 0, '30 minutes', '115', '15 minutes', 'hour');
