(172, 24, 'The Psychic Reading on Healing That Needs to Be Done - 1 hour', 'The Psychic Reading on Healing That Needs to Be Done session is a focused and intuitive experience designed to uncover areas in your life that require healing. Whether it\'s emotional wounds, physical imbalances, spiritual disconnect, or energetic blockages, this session allows you to gain clarity on the specific healing work that needs to be addressed in order to move forward in a balanced, healthy, and empowered way. By channeling insights from your higher self, spirit guides, or loved ones, we will explore what is holding you back, and how to heal and release these obstacles in alignment with your soul\'s highest good.\r\n\r\nWhat to Expect:\r\nPsychic Reading on Healing Areas: Using my intuitive abilities, I will focus on the healing that needs to be done in your life. This may involve exploring different aspects such as:\r\n\r\nEmotional Healing: Identifying past emotional wounds, trauma, grief, or unresolved feelings that need attention and healing.\r\nPhysical Healing: Pinpointing areas of physical discomfort or illness that may have an emotional or spiritual cause.\r\nSpiritual Healing: Exploring areas where you may feel disconnected from your higher self, purpose, or the divine. This could include feelings of spiritual stagnation, a lack of direction, or disconnection from your intuition.\r\nEnergetic Blockages: Assessing your energy field (aura) for any blockages or stagnant energy that may be preventing the flow of positive energy and manifesting as challenges in your life.\r\n\r\nDuring this portion, you may receive information such as:\r\n\r\nThe root cause of your healing needs, whether from past experiences, ancestral patterns, or karmic imprints.\r\nSpecific emotions or beliefs that are keeping you stuck.\r\nInsights into how certain relationships or life situations are contributing to your current state of imbalance.\r\n\r\nHealing Recommendations &amp; Guidance: After identifying the areas of healing that need attention, I will provide detailed guidance on how to address them. This could include:\r\n\r\nReleasing Negative Patterns: Techniques or advice on releasing limiting beliefs, past traumas, or negative emotions that are holding you back from healing.\r\nHealing Tools and Practices: Suggestions for specific healing practices that resonate with you, such as meditation, energy healing, chakra balancing, or journaling.\r\nSelf-Care Practices: Personalized recommendations on how to nurture yourself physically, emotionally, and spiritually to support your healing journey. This may include the use of affirmations, visualization techniques, or practices to create healthier boundaries.\r\nSpiritual &amp; Energy Healing: Insights on whether you need specific energetic work such as chakra healing, aura cleansing, or working with healing crystals or sacred symbols.\r\nEnergy Healing &amp; Cleansing (if applicable): Depending on the psychic reading, there may be an opportunity for me to perform an energy healing or cleansing during the session. This may include:\r\n\r\nAura Cleansing: Clearing any negative or stagnant energy from your aura and energy field.\r\nChakra Healing: Restoring balance to your chakras, helping to clear any blockages and align your energy centers.\r\nCord Cutting: Releasing any unhealthy energetic attachments or cords that may be contributing to your emotional pain or spiritual disconnection.\r\nReiki or Healing Energy Channeling: Sending healing energy to areas of your life that need transformation and balance.\r\nIntegration &amp; Healing Plan: After the psychic insights and healing work, we will create an integration plan. This will help you move forward in your healing process with clear steps and actionable items. I will guide you on how to incorporate the healing messages and practices into your daily life to ensure lasting transformation.\r\n\r\nBenefits of the Psychic Reading on Healing That Needs to Be Done:\r\n\r\nClarity on Healing Needs: Gain insight into which areas of your life require immediate healing and attention, whether emotional, physical, spiritual, or energetic.\r\nEmotional Release: Let go of past traumas, grief, and limiting beliefs that are preventing you from living a fully empowered life.\r\nSpiritual Growth: Reconnect with your spiritual purpose and higher self, clearing any obstacles preventing you from stepping into your full potential.\r\nEmpowerment: Receive clear guidance on how to take charge of your own healing and make positive changes in your life.\r\nPersonalized Healing Plan: Walk away with a practical plan for your healing journey, tailored to your unique needs.\r\n\r\nWho Can Benefit:\r\n\r\nThis session is ideal for anyone who feels stuck, overwhelmed, or disconnected from their true self and purpose. If you are experiencing emotional distress, physical discomfort, spiritual confusion, or simply need clarity on the healing you need to do, this session can provide the insights and guidance you are seeking. It is especially helpful for:\r\n\r\nIndividuals seeking emotional healing or wanting to process grief, trauma, or past pain.\r\nPeople who are feeling spiritually lost or disconnected.\r\nThose experiencing physical symptoms that may have an energetic or emotional cause.\r\nAnyone looking to deepen their self-awareness and empower their healing process.\r\n\r\nThe Psychic Reading on Healing That Needs to Be Done session offers you the clarity, guidance, and healing you need to release what no longer serves you and step into a new chapter of growth, empowerment, and wholeness. Let this session be a catalyst for deep transformation and healing.', 'The Psychic Reading on Healing That Needs to Be Done session is a focused and intuitive experience designed to uncover areas in your life that require healing. Whether it\'s emotional wounds, physical imbalances, spiritual disconnect, or energetic blockages, this session allows you to gain clarity on the specific healing work that needs to be addressed in order to move forward in a balanced, healthy, and empowered way. By channeling insights from your higher self, spirit guides, or loved ones, we will explore what is holding you back, and how to heal and release these obstacles in alignment with your soul\'s highest good.', NULL, '[\"4\",\"6\",\"7\"]', '[\"13\",\"35\",\"37\",\"39\",\"40\",\"61\"]', '1742400456_copy.jpg', '2025-03-19 16:07:36', '2025-03-19 16:09:33', 'virtual', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '150', NULL, '48', NULL, NULL, 1, '24 hour', 0, '30 minutes', '115', '15 minutes', 'hour'),
(173, 24, 'Cord Cutting Healing Session - 1 Hour', 'The Cord Cutting Healing session is a powerful and transformative spiritual practice designed to help you release unhealthy energetic attachments or \"cords\" that may be draining your energy, causing emotional distress, or keeping you tied to past relationships, events, or experiences. These energetic cords are often formed between individuals, situations, or aspects of ourselves and can create imbalances, blockages, or a sense of being stuck. This session will assist you in cutting these cords and freeing yourself from any negative influences, allowing you to restore your energy, reclaim your power, and move forward with clarity and purpose.\r\n\r\nWhat to Expect:\r\n\r\nEnergy Assessment &amp; Identification of Cords: Through intuitive guidance, I will identify the energetic cords that are present. These cords may be tied to:\r\n\r\nPast relationships (romantic, familial, or friendships)\r\nNegative patterns, beliefs, or habits\r\nUnresolved trauma or emotional pain\r\nToxic people or situations draining your energy\r\nAttachments to past versions of yourself or unhealed wounds\r\nYou may be invited to reflect on the specific people or events in your life that you feel bound to, allowing us to focus on those connections that need healing.\r\n\r\nCord Cutting Process: The core of the session involves cutting the energetic cords. This is done using various healing tools or techniques, such as:\r\n\r\nEnergetic Visualization: A guided process where you will visualize the cords being severed, releasing the connection and any emotional or energetic attachments.\r\nShamanic Healing: Using drumming, chanting, or sacred rituals to cut the cords and remove unwanted energies from your energy field.\r\nHealing &amp; Releasing Blocked Energy: As the cords are cut, we will also focus on healing any emotional wounds, traumas, or unresolved feelings that may have been holding you in place. This may involve working with your chakras or energy centers to clear out blockages and restore balance. You may feel a sense of relief, lightness, or peace as the energy is freed.\r\n\r\nReconnection to Your True Self: After the cords are cut and the energy is cleared, we will focus on reconnecting you to your highest self and reinforcing healthy, empowering connections. You will be guided to feel your energy flowing freely and fully, reclaiming your personal power and setting boundaries for healthy relationships moving forward.\r\n\r\nGrounding &amp; Integration: The session will conclude with a grounding practice to help you anchor the healing energy into your physical body and energy field. This will allow you to integrate the shifts and continue with a sense of balance and clarity. You may be provided with suggestions for maintaining your energetic boundaries, such as using affirmations, meditation, or visualization techniques.\r\n\r\nBenefits of Cord Cutting Healing:\r\n\r\nEmotional Freedom: Let go of past emotional baggage, guilt, or resentment tied to past relationships or experiences.\r\nEnergy Restoration: Release negative attachments and energetic blockages, allowing your energy to flow freely and restore balance.\r\nSpiritual Healing: Clear spiritual or karmic ties that may be holding you back or keeping you in repetitive cycles.\r\nPersonal Empowerment: Reclaim your personal power and create healthy boundaries in relationships.\r\nRelease of Toxic Patterns: Break free from toxic behaviors or relationships that drain your energy or hinder your personal growth.\r\nGreater Clarity &amp; Focus: By cutting the energetic cords, you may experience increased mental clarity and emotional stability, helping you make better decisions and move forward with confidence.\r\nImproved Relationships: Heal and release unhealthy attachments, allowing you to form more loving, supportive, and balanced relationships.\r\n\r\nWho Can Benefit:\r\n\r\nThis Cord Cutting Healing session is ideal for anyone feeling emotionally drained, stuck in negative patterns, or affected by past relationships or events. Whether you are struggling with unhealthy connections, unresolved traumas, or simply feel like you’re carrying the weight of past emotional baggage, this session can help you release those energetic ties and step into a more empowered and balanced state. It is especially helpful for:\r\n\r\nThose who have experienced difficult or toxic relationships (romantic, familial, or professional).\r\nPeople dealing with grief, loss, or past trauma that still impacts their current life.\r\nIndividuals seeking to create more space for personal growth and healing.\r\nAnyone feeling energetically drained or blocked, especially after interacting with certain people or situations.\r\nStep into your power, cut the cords that bind you, and experience emotional freedom with this transformative healing session. Reclaim your energy, clarity, and peace as you move forward with renewed strength and purpose.', 'The Cord Cutting Healing session is a powerful and transformative spiritual practice designed to help you release unhealthy energetic attachments or \"cords\" that may be draining your energy, causing emotional distress, or keeping you tied to past relationships, events, or experiences. These energetic cords are often formed between individuals, situations, or aspects of ourselves and can create imbalances, blockages, or a sense of being stuck. This session will assist you in cutting these cords and freeing yourself from any negative influences, allowing you to restore your energy, reclaim your power, and move forward with clarity and purpose.', NULL, '[\"4\",\"6\",\"7\"]', '[\"80\",\"81\"]', '1742401358.jpg', '2025-03-19 16:22:38', '2025-03-19 16:22:38', 'virtual', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '150', NULL, '48', NULL, NULL, 1, '24 hour', 0, '1 hour', '115', '15 minutes', 'hour'),
(174, 24, 'Chakra Alignment Session - 30 Minutes', 'This Chakra Alignment session is designed to harmonize and balance the nine main energy centers (chakras) of your body, promoting overall health, well-being, and spiritual growth. By aligning your chakras, we help restore the natural flow of energy throughout your body, releasing blockages that may be affecting your physical, emotional, or mental state. This session is perfect for anyone looking to enhance their energy, improve their emotional balance, and deepen their connection to their higher self.\r\n\r\nWhat to Expect:\r\n\r\nIntroduction &amp; Intention Setting: We will begin by discussing your current physical, emotional, or spiritual concerns. We will set an intention for the session that aligns with your goals, whether it’s to release stress, find emotional clarity, or increase vitality. This creates a focused and personalized approach to your chakra healing.\r\n\r\nGrounding &amp; Relaxation: The session will begin with a grounding meditation to help you relax deeply. This prepares your mind and body to open up to the healing process, allowing you to feel centered and connected to the earth.\r\n\r\nChakra Assessment: I will guide you through a gentle assessment of each of your seven main chakras:\r\n\r\nEarth Star Charka - I Ground\r\nRoot Chakra – I Am\r\nSacral Chakra  – I Feel\r\nSolar Plexus Chakra - I Can\r\nHeart Chakra - I Love\r\nThroat Chakra - I Speak\r\nThird Eye Chakra - I See\r\nCrown Chakra - I Know\r\nSoul Star Chakra - I Connect\r\n\r\nDuring this process, I will intuitively sense and identify areas of imbalance or blockages within these chakras, which may manifest as physical discomfort, emotional pain, or mental confusion.\r\n\r\nChakra Clearing &amp; Balancing: Using a combination of energy healing techniques, I will work to clear blockages, excess energy, or imbalances in each chakra, all with your consent. This may include:\r\n\r\nEnergy channeling\r\nGuided visualization or breathing exercises\r\nSound healing, such as tuning forks or singing bowls, which can help align and balance the energetic centers\r\nAs each chakra is balanced, you may feel sensations of warmth, tingling, or a deep sense of relaxation.\r\n\r\n\r\nIntegration &amp; Closing: The session will conclude with a brief grounding exercise to help you integrate the balanced energy. I will offer recommendations for practices you can do at home to keep your chakras aligned, such as meditation, breathing exercises, or lifestyle adjustments.\r\n\r\nBenefits of Chakra Alignment:\r\n\r\nEmotional Healing: Clears emotional blockages.\r\nMental Clarity: Improves focus, reduces mental fog, and enhances intuition and creativity.\r\nSpiritual Growth: Deepens your connection to your higher self, encouraging personal growth and spiritual awakening.\r\n\r\nThis Chakra Alignment session is a powerful tool for anyone looking to reset their energetic system, clear out negative patterns, and reconnect with their inner power. Whether you’re seeking relief from stress, improving emotional health, or enhancing your spiritual journey, this session will guide you back into balance, leaving you feeling refreshed, revitalized, and energetically aligned.', 'This Chakra Alignment session is designed to harmonize and balance the nine main energy centers (chakras) of your body, promoting overall health, well-being, and spiritual growth. By aligning your chakras, we help restore the natural flow of energy throughout your body, releasing blockages that may be affecting your physical, emotional, or mental state. This session is perfect for anyone looking to enhance their energy, improve their emotional balance, and deepen their connection to their higher self.\r\n\r\nEarth Star Charka - I Ground\r\nRoot Chakra – I Am\r\nSacral Chakra  – I Feel\r\nSolar Plexus Chakra - I Can\r\nHeart Chakra - I Love\r\nThroat Chakra - I Speak\r\nThird Eye Chakra - I See\r\nCrown Chakra - I Know\r\nSoul Star Chakra - I Connect', NULL, '[\"4\",\"6\",\"7\"]', '[\"14\",\"35\",\"37\",\"61\"]', '1742401480.jpg', '2025-03-19 16:24:40', '2025-03-19 16:24:40', 'virtual', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '75', NULL, '48', NULL, NULL, 1, '24 hour', 0, '30 minutes', '115', '15 minutes', 'hour'),
(175, 79, 'Mini Reset (15-Min 1 on 1)', 'In just 15 minutes, we\'ll guide you through a focused breathwork practice designed to release tension, clear your mind, and re-energize your day. Perfect for those busy moments when you need to reset and refocus on the go.\r\n\r\nDuring these sessions, we will do self-healing, affirmations, breath work, and of course, TONS of guided visualizations.', 'Need a quick mental refresh? The Mini Reset session is your go-to for instant clarity and calm.', NULL, '[\"4\",\"9\"]', '[\"11\",\"24\",\"31\",\"79\"]', '1742401773.png', '2025-03-19 16:29:33', '2025-03-19 16:35:36', 'virtual', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '20', NULL, NULL, 'Your Mini Reset is Confirmed! Here’s What to Expect 💜\r\nThank you for booking your Mini Reset (15-Min 1-on-1) session! I’m so excited to guide you through this quick yet powerful BreathPlay™ experience to help you release tension, clear your mind, and step into a space of clarity and calm.\r\n\r\nWhat to Expect:\r\n🌿 A guided breath practice to refresh your energy\r\n💭 Powerful affirmations to realign your mindset\r\n✨ Self-healing techniques & visualizations to reset your focus\r\n\r\nHow to Prepare:\r\nFind a quiet, comfortable space where you won’t be disturbed.\r\nWear something comfy and bring a glass of water.\r\nArrive a few minutes early to settle in.\r\nIf you have any questions before our session, feel free to reach out. Can’t wait to guide you through this moment of renewal!\r\n\r\nKingsley', NULL, 1, '24 hour', 0, '15 minutes', '115', '15 minutes', 'minute'),
(176, 24, 'Embrace the Dark Goddess: A Journey of Healing, Release, and Transformation - 1 Hour', 'In the midst of darkness, when life feels heavy and uncertain, there is a powerful force waiting to guide you through the shadows—the Dark Goddess. Often misunderstood, she is not a symbol of fear, but of profound transformation and healing. When you are at your lowest, when the path forward seems unclear, it is in these moments that the Dark Goddess finds you, offering wisdom, strength, and the courage to rise from the depths of despair.\r\n\r\nThe Dark Goddess Finds Us in Our Darkness. We all encounter times of darkness in our lives—moments of grief, loss, confusion, or struggle. These are the times when we feel disconnected from our true selves and from the world around us. It is in these very moments that the Dark Goddess appears, inviting us into a deep, spiritual awakening. Her presence is not one of judgment but of profound understanding and compassion. The Dark Goddess does not fear darkness; she embodies it. She understands that in the depths of shadow, there are lessons to be learned. She teaches us that darkness is not a place to run from, but a space to embrace and transform. She helps us navigate through our fears, confront our past wounds, and ultimately emerge stronger, wiser, and more aligned with our true essence.\r\n\r\nWorking with the Dark Goddess is a sacred journey of self-discovery and healing. She calls us to surrender, to look within, and to confront the hidden parts of ourselves that need attention. Through this process, we learn to heal old wounds, release limiting beliefs, and awaken to the power that has always been within us. The Dark Goddess offers us the tools to break free from the cycles that have kept us trapped in pain and confusion. Whether it is through guided healing rituals, meditations, or spiritual practices, she teaches us how to honor our shadows and transform them into strength.\r\n\r\nHer wisdom is rooted in acceptance and compassion, guiding us gently, yet powerfully, toward the light. Working with the Dark Goddess means learning to integrate both light and shadow into our being, accepting our imperfections, and embracing our full power as women, as healers, and as divine beings.\r\n\r\n\r\nIf you feel called to connect with the Dark Goddess and embark on a transformative healing journey, you are not alone. This is a path of courage, self-love, and empowerment. Through Dark Goddess Healing sessions, you can learn how to navigate your own darkness with grace and strength. You do not need to face your challenges alone. Together, we will work with the energies of the Dark Goddess to help you heal, release old wounds, and step fully into your power. It’s time to leave behind the darkness that has weighed you down and step into the light of your true self.\r\n\r\nAre you ready to embrace the wisdom of the Dark Goddess and begin your journey of transformation? Book a session today and discover the healing power that awaits you.', 'Working with the Dark Goddess is a sacred journey of self-discovery and healing. She calls us to surrender, to look within, and to confront the hidden parts of ourselves that need attention. Through this process, we learn to heal old wounds, release limiting beliefs, and awaken to the power that has always been within us. The Dark Goddess offers us the tools to break free from the cycles that have kept us trapped in pain and confusion. Whether it is through guided healing rituals, meditations, or spiritual practices, she teaches us how to honor our shadows and transform them into strength. If you feel called to connect with the Dark Goddess and embark on a transformative healing journey, you are not alone. This is a path of courage, self-love, and empowerment. Through Dark Goddess Healing sessions, you can learn how to navigate your own darkness with grace and strength. You do not need to face your challenges alone. Together, we will work with the energies of the Dark Goddess to help you heal, release old wounds, and step fully into your power. It’s time to leave behind the darkness that has weighed you down and step into the light of your true self.', NULL, '[\"4\",\"6\",\"7\"]', '[\"35\",\"36\",\"37\",\"61\"]', '1742401814.jpg', '2025-03-19 16:30:14', '2025-03-19 16:30:14', 'virtual', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '150', NULL, '48', NULL, NULL, 1, '24 hour', 0, '1 hour', '115', '15 minutes', 'hour'),
(177, 79, 'Full Serenity (30-Min 1 on 1)', 'In just 30 minutes, we\'ll take you on a journey of extended breathwork, helping you connect more deeply with your body and mind. This session is ideal for unwinding after a long day, preparing for a peaceful night\'s sleep, or whenever you need to fully center yourself in the present moment. Experience the full benefits of breathwork and leave feeling balanced, calm, and rejuvenated.\r\n\r\nDuring these sessions, we will do self-healing, affirmations, breath work, and of course, TONS of guided visualizations.', 'Immerse yourself in a deeper state of relaxation and inner peace with our Full Serenity session.', NULL, '[\"4\",\"7\"]', '[\"11\",\"15\",\"24\",\"25\",\"31\",\"79\"]', '1742401945.png', '2025-03-19 16:32:25', '2025-03-19 16:32:25', 'virtual', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '50', NULL, NULL, 'Your Full Serenity Session is Confirmed! 💜\r\n\r\nThank you for booking your Full Serenity (30-Min 1-on-1) session! This is your time to fully unwind, reconnect, and immerse yourself in deep relaxation. Over the next 30 minutes, we’ll guide you through an extended BreathPlay™ experience designed to bring balance, clarity, and calm to your mind and body.\r\n\r\nWhat to Expect:\r\n🌬️ A deeper, more intentional breathwork practice\r\n💫 Self-healing techniques to release stress and tension\r\n💭 Affirmations & guided visualizations for peace and clarity\r\n\r\nHow to Prepare:\r\nFind a quiet, comfortable space where you can fully relax.\r\nWear cozy clothing and have a glass of water nearby.\r\nConsider lighting a candle, dimming the lights, or playing soft music to enhance your experience.\r\nArrive a few minutes early to settle in and breathe before we begin.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions leading up to your session, don’t hesitate to reach out. I can’t wait to guide you on this journey of serenity and renewal!\r\n\r\nKingsley', NULL, 1, '24 hour', 0, '30 minutes', '115', '15 minutes', 'minute'),
(178, 79, 'Introduction To BreathPlay™ Session (15-Min 1 on 1)', 'This Introduction to BreathPlay™ session is the perfect starting point! In this personalized 1-on-1 experience, you\'ll explore the fundamentals of breathwork, guided visualization, and self-healing techniques. Whether you\'re new to breathwork or looking for a fresh approach, this session will help you release stress, increase mindfulness, and feel more aligned in your daily life. Walk away with simple yet powerful breathing techniques you can use anytime for clarity, calm, and energy renewal.', 'Curious about BreathPlay™ and how it can transform your well-being?\r\nFOR FIRST TIME BOOKERS ONLY.', NULL, '[\"4\",\"6\",\"9\"]', '[\"11\",\"15\",\"24\",\"25\",\"31\",\"79\"]', '1742402111.png', '2025-03-19 16:35:11', '2025-03-19 16:37:36', 'virtual', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '15', NULL, '15', 'Welcome to BreathPlay™ - Your Session is Confirmed 💜\r\nThank you for booking your Introduction to BreathPlay™ (1-on-1) Session! I’m so excited to guide you through this experience and introduce you to the powerful practice of BreathPlay™. This session will help you connect with your breath, release stress, and discover techniques that you can integrate into your daily life for more clarity, calm, and balance.\r\n\r\nWhat to Expect:\r\n🌿 A gentle introduction to breathwork and its benefits\r\n💫 Self-healing techniques to help you feel more grounded\r\n💭 Guided visualizations and affirmations to create inner peace\r\n✨ Simple breathing exercises you can use anytime, anywhere\r\n\r\nHow to Prepare:\r\nFind a quiet, comfortable space where you can focus without distractions.\r\nWear something comfortable and bring a glass of water.\r\nArrive a few minutes early to settle in and relax before we begin.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions before our session, feel free to reach out. I can’t wait to guide you on this journey toward breath, balance, and self-discovery!\r\n\r\nKingsley', NULL, 1, '24 hour', 0, '15 minutes', '115', '15 minutes', 'minute'),
(179, 24, 'Celtic Shamanic Healing/ Activation - 30 Minutes', 'The Celtic Shamanic Healing and Activation session is a deeply transformative spiritual experience that draws upon the ancient wisdom and healing practices of the Celtic tradition. Rooted in the sacred connection to nature, the elements, ancestors, and the spiritual realm, this session is designed to activate your inner power, restore balance, and guide you toward healing, growth, and spiritual awakening. Through the lens of Celtic shamanism, we will work with sacred energies, tools, and rituals to heal the soul, restore energy, and reconnect you to the ancient wisdom within.\r\n\r\nWhat to Expect:\r\nSacred Opening &amp; Setting the Intention: Before we meet, Candice will begin the session by calling in the four sacred directions—East, South, West, and North—along with the elemental forces of Earth, Air, Fire, and Water. This ritual invites the presence of the ancestors, spirit guides, and the protective energies of the natural world. Insights will be shared for the healing, whether it’s to release old wounds, awaken your ancestral power, or find deeper alignment with your life path.\r\n\r\nCeltic Journeying: Using the sacred method of shamanic journeying, we will enter an altered state of consciousness through guided visualization. This journey will connect you with the spiritual realms, where you may encounter your ancestors, animal spirit guides, or divine beings. Key aspects of this journey include:\r\n\r\nAncestral Healing &amp; Wisdom: Channeling the knowledge and guidance of your ancestors to uncover hidden gifts, healing wisdom, or messages from the past.\r\nPower Animal Connection: Connecting with your animal spirit guides to receive strength, protection, and guidance for your journey.\r\nSoul Retrieval: If there are parts of your soul that have been lost due to trauma or unresolved emotions, we will call back those fragments to restore your energetic wholeness.\r\nSacred Visioning: In this space, you may receive visions, symbols, or messages that provide insight into your life purpose, relationships, or spiritual path.\r\nElemental Healing: The Celtic tradition places a deep emphasis on the healing power of the elements. Throughout the session, we will work with the energies of the Earth, Air, Fire, and Water to cleanse, balance, and activate your energy. Each element will guide a specific aspect of your healing:\r\n\r\nEarth: Grounding and healing your body, helping you release negative energies and reconnect with your physical self.\r\nAir: Clearing mental blockages, enhancing clarity, and promoting wisdom through the mind.\r\nFire: Igniting your personal power, creativity, and inner passion, helping you step into your full potential.\r\nWater: Emotional healing, purification, and release of old emotional wounds or stagnation.\r\nSacred Tools &amp; Rituals: The session may incorporate traditional Celtic healing tools such as:\r\n\r\nActivation of Ancestral Power &amp; Spiritual Gifts: One of the core aspects of this session is the activation of your inner spiritual gifts. Through the guidance of your ancestors and spiritual guides, we will work together to activate your intuition, spiritual abilities, and ancestral wisdom. This may involve:\r\n\r\nReawakening your intuitive abilities such as clairvoyance, clairaudience, or healing powers.\r\nDiscovering hidden talents and strengths that connect you to your heritage and lineage.\r\nEmpowering you to step into your spiritual purpose with confidence and clarity.\r\n\r\nGrounding &amp; Integration: At the end of the session, we will perform a grounding ritual to anchor the healing energy into your physical body. This ensures that the spiritual insights, energies, and activations received during the journey are fully integrated and aligned. You will be encouraged to connect with the Earth, allowing the healing to flow through you and stay with you long after the session ends.\r\n\r\nBenefits of the Celtic Shamanic Healing and Activation:\r\n\r\nAncestral Healing: Connect with the healing wisdom of your ancestors to release inherited patterns and awaken forgotten gifts.\r\nEmotional &amp; Spiritual Transformation: Heal deep emotional wounds, clear energetic blockages, and activate a sense of inner peace and spiritual clarity.\r\nEnergy Activation: Awaken dormant spiritual gifts and strengthen your connection to the spiritual realm, enhancing your intuitive and healing abilities.\r\nAlignment with Nature’s Cycles: Reconnect with the rhythms of the natural world, helping you live in greater alignment with your true self and the flow of life.\r\nPersonal Empowerment: Restore your inner strength, confidence, and connection to your purpose, enabling you to live a life of power, purpose, and balance.\r\n\r\nWho Can Benefit:\r\n\r\nThe Celtic Shamanic Healing and Activation session is perfect for anyone seeking to reconnect with their ancestral roots, heal past wounds, or activate their spiritual gifts. It’s ideal for those looking for deep emotional healing, spiritual growth, and a reconnection to the wisdom and energies of the natural world. Whether you feel disconnected, stuck, or in need of guidance, this session offers a powerful path to spiritual awakening and personal empowerment.\r\n\r\nStep into the ancient healing traditions of the Celtic people, awaken your ancestral wisdom, and activate your inner power with this deeply transformative shamanic healing experience.', 'The Celtic Shamanic Healing and Activation session is a deeply transformative spiritual experience that draws upon the ancient wisdom and healing practices of the Celtic tradition. Rooted in the sacred connection to nature, the elements, ancestors, and the spiritual realm, this session is designed to activate your inner power, restore balance, and guide you toward healing, growth, and spiritual awakening. Through the lens of Celtic shamanism, we will work with sacred energies, tools, and rituals to heal the soul, restore energy, and reconnect you to the ancient wisdom within.', NULL, '[\"4\",\"6\",\"7\"]', '[\"35\",\"37\",\"61\",\"82\",\"83\"]', '1742402287.jpg', '2025-03-19 16:38:07', '2025-03-19 16:38:07', 'virtual', NULL, NULL, 1, NULL, '75', NULL, '48', NULL, NULL, 1, '24 hour', 0, '30 minutes', '115', '15 minutes', 'hour'),
