(51, 'Lauren Best', 'Lauren', 'Best', NULL, 'Lauren Best is a Certified Hypnotherapist, Transformation Designer, and the Founder of Possibilities Universe. She helps people break free from perfectionism, self-sabotage, and limiting beliefs by reconnecting with their intuition, celebrating themselves, and embracing their fullest potential.\r\n\r\nLauren’s approach to hypnotherapy is rooted in helping people release the pressure of external expectations and find momentum through self-trust, joy, and experimentation. With a deep understanding of how perfectionism and internalized \'not enoughness\' can hold people back, Lauren uses hypnosis to rewire the subconscious mind, offering clients new pathways toward self-worth, creativity, and freedom.\r\n\r\nHer journey toward becoming a hypnotherapist was shaped by her own experience of navigating environments that didn’t quite fit. With a background in product and furniture design in London and a career in business transformation design in Singapore, Lauren often felt drawn toward doing things differently. This desire to break free from traditional molds eventually led her to create Possibilities Universe — a space designed to inspire self-trust, creative experimentation, and self-celebration.\r\n\r\nLauren’s signature Celebrate Yourself Card Deck was born from this mission, encouraging people to pause, acknowledge their progress, and honour their inner voice. Alongside her private hypnotherapy sessions, she also facilitates group workshops, guided visualizations, and creative experiences that help individuals pursue their most authentic dreams without fear of failure.\r\n\r\nLauren believes the subconscious mind holds the key to unlocking untapped potential. By helping her clients rewrite old narratives, she supports them in overcoming self-doubt, fear of success, and internalized pressure. Her work offers a safe space for people to dream bigger, trust themselves, and celebrate every step of their journey — imperfections and all.', '[\"115\",\"116\",\"118\",\"374\",\"884\"]', 'hello@lauren-best.com', NULL, '$2y$12$BLRk4kKidRSRwTvNB69XU.Prisbm2VdqMGbP3XzGK4TVh0HQlvRiu', NULL, '2025-03-02 05:16:16', '2025-03-11 00:03:57', 1, 1),
