ation Protection and Electronic Documents Act (PIPEDA) to protect client data.\r\n\r\n6. Limitation of Liability\r\nWe are not responsible for any personal, financial, or health outcomes resulting from our coaching services. Clients accept full responsibility for their actions. By using our services, clients waive any claims against us for damages or losses.\r\n\r\n7. Compliance with Canadian Laws\r\nOur coaching services comply with relevant Canadian laws, including business and consumer protection regulations. Any disputes will be handled under the jurisdiction of Ontario, Canada.\r\n\r\n8. Changes to These Terms\r\nWe may update these terms as needed. The latest version will always be available on our website. Continued use of our services after updates constitutes acceptance of the new terms.\r\n\r\n9. Contact Information\r\nFor any questions, please contact: Jothi Creative Wellness Inc., info@jothi.ca, 905-239-0078', '2025-03-02 05:16:09', '2025-03-19 02:03:45', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":\"11:00\",\"to\":\"14:00\"},\"every_wednesday\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":\"11:00\",\"to\":\"14:00\"},\"every_thursday\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":\"11:00\",\"to\":\"14:00\"},\"every_friday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"weekends_only_-_every_sat_&_sundays\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null}}', 'All booking cancellations must happen within 48 hours of the booking or a full charge may apply.'),
