(31, 31, 'Hi, I’m Alyria (they/them) I am a proud parent of two boys and an experienced Reiki Master, Sound Practitioner, and lightworker based in Victoria, British Columbia, Canada. Guided by a holistic approach to healing, I create transformative spaces that align the mind, body, and spirit. Through sound, energy, and spiritual practices, I strive to support and empower my clients on their journey to well-being, self-discovery, and inner harmony.', 'Rainbow Vibrations', '[\"116\"]', '[]', '{\"profile_image\":\"1740904231_IMG_0351-scaled.jpeg\"}', 'Welcome! My name is Alyria (they/them)\r\n\r\nI am a seasoned Reiki Master, sound practitioner, and lightworker based in Victoria, British Columbia, Canada. My work is rooted in creating transformative spaces where sound, energy, and spirituality intertwine to support your well-being on every level—mind, body, and spirit. I invite you to explore your inner world through sacred soundscapes, intentional rituals, and powerful energetic practices that foster self-discovery, rejuvenation, and connection.\r\n\r\nAs a clairvoyant, clairaudient, claircognizant, and clairsentient starseed, my mission is to guide you in reconnecting with your highest self and finding your unique spiritual truth. By channeling light language, and energy directly fom source, I can activate and positively reprogram DNA, helping to raise your vibration and align you with your divine purpose. My earthly incarnation is dedicated to raising the frequency of Mother Earth and serving as a beacon of light for the collective.\r\n\r\nIn every session, I blend the gentle, restorative energy of Reiki with the transformative power of crystal singing bowls and other instruments. This work is not about fixing or healing you—you are already whole. My role is to hold space for your journey, reminding you of your innate ability to heal, thrive, and access your inner wisdom. Together, we create an inclusive and supportive environment where you can experience clarity, peace, and inner harmony.\r\n\r\nMy personal healing journey began in 2013, when I left a toxic relationship while caring for my infant son. That pivotal moment led me to Reiki and, soon after, to the profound resonance of sound meditations. Since 2017, I have worked with crystal singing bowls, deepened my practice with over 30 hours of intensive sound training, and discovered the transformative power of these modalities to guide myself and others toward balance and connection.\r\n\r\nI work with people across all walks of life, including those navigating pregnancy, postpartum, grief, life-transitions, or simply seeking rest and rejuvenation. Whether we are working to release what no longer serves you or to create a space for deep relaxation, my passion is to ensure you feel seen, heard, and empowered on your healing path.\r\n\r\nOutside of my practice, I find inspiration in creative, artistic and musical pursuits, the natural world, and the joy of motherhood. My two sons and the beauty of nature are my greatest sources of love and creativity. You might also find me challenging myself at my local bouldering gym, exploring the connection between my body and spirit in new ways.\r\n\r\nIt is an honour to walk this path with you. Illuminating you journey to inner harmony.\r\n\r\nI acknowledge and offer respect to the traditional territory of the Lək̓ʷəŋən (Lekwungen) People, known as the Esquimalt and Songhees First Nations, part of the Coast Salish Territory, in which we live and learn upon here in Victoria, BC.', NULL, '5,6,10,14,15,16,17,18,19,20,21,22,65,66,68,96,97,119,123,126,127,130,132,142,143,144,168,169,176,186,214,236,302,318,319,320,321,322,323,324,326,327,328', '2,3,4,5,6,7', '[]', '11,12', 'America/Creston', NULL, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-03-02 05:16:12', '2025-03-10 07:12:07', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_wednesday\":{\"from\":null,\"t