(32, 32, 'Sarah Campbell – Founder of Me B4 We Coaching\r\n\r\nSarah Campbell is a certified sex coach, clinical sexologist, and registered early childhood educator dedicated to helping single moms reconnect with their sexual selves and embrace a life of confidence, pleasure, and empowerment. With over a decade of experience in intimacy coaching and a passion for supporting women, Sarah founded Me B4 We Coaching to provide a holistic, personalized approach to sexual wellness and self-discovery.\r\n\r\nSarah’s coaching philosophy is rooted in the belief that the most important relationship you have is with yourself—and when you nurture that connection, you create the foundation for deeper, more fulfilling relationships with others. She specializes in guiding clients through challenges such as mixed libido, sexless relationships, sexual inhibition, body confidence, orgasm discovery, intimacy communication, and dating concerns.\r\n\r\nThrough one-on-one coaching, educational workshops, customized exercises, and practical resources, Sarah helps clients break through societal pressures and personal barriers that hold them back from fully experiencing pleasure. Her approach is compassionate, shame-free, and tailored to each individual’s needs, creating a safe space where moms can rediscover their desires without guilt or judgment.\r\n\r\nIn addition to her work as a sex coach, Sarah is also focused on helping single moms achieve financial freedom through online digital marketing. She understands the unique challenges of balancing motherhood, personal growth, and financial independence, which is why she offers guidance on building flexible, online businesses that fit into a busy mom’s lifestyle. Her goal is to empower women to reclaim their confidence—not just in the bedroom, but in their everyday lives.\r\n\r\nWith a background that includes working on 20 cruise ships across five different cruise lines, Sarah has extensive experience supporting diverse individuals and families. She has also served as a youth counselor, program supervisor, and Make-A-Wish ambassador, demonstrating her deep commitment to helping others navigate life’s transitions.\r\n\r\nSarah’s work is not just about intimacy—it’s about redefining pleasure, self-worth, and personal fulfillment. Whether coaching a mom through a sexless marriage, helping her embrace body confidence after childbirth, or guiding her toward financial stability, Sarah is committed to transforming lives.\r\n\r\nAre you ready to step out of “mom mode” and back into you? From motherhood to empowerment, your journey back to pleasure starts now.\r\n\r\nLearn more at Me B4 We Coaching and take the first step toward a life filled with confidence, intimacy, and self-love.', NULL, '[\"897\"]', '[\"71\",\"72\",\"78\"]', '{\"profile_image\":\"1742266005_BC250807-A55E-4DB7-93C2-B50873AB8A1E.png\"}', NULL, NULL, '344,345,346,347,348,349', '8,169,170,171,172,173,174', '[\"5\",\"6\",\"9\"]', '90,91,92', 'America/Toronto', '[\"Virtual offerings\",\"Office-based sessions\",\"Payment plans\"]', 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-03-02 05:16:13', '2025-03-18 02:48:26', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_wednesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_thursday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_friday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"weekends_only_-_every_sat_&_sundays\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null}}', NULL),
(33, 33, 'Hi, I\'m Anna Silfa, a Wellness Therapist based in Ottawa, Ontario. Specializing in Essential Emotions coaching, Reiki energy healing, and the Aromatouch Technique, I am passionate about guiding others toward holistic well-being. My approach focuses on creating a warm, welcoming space for clients to reconnect with their physical, emotional, and spiritual balance. I eagerly anticipate the opportunity to connect with you and embark on this transformative journey together!', 'Anna Silfa Wellness', '[\"371\"]', '[]', '{\"profile_image\":\"1740910544_SN103907-Copy.jpg\"}', 'In today’s fast-paced world, I believe in the power of pausing to rediscover our inner balance. Through Essential Emotions Coaching, Reiki Energy Healing, and Aromatherapy, I guide individuals on a transformative journey toward relaxation, clarity, and harmony—restoring the natural equilibrium of body, mind, and spirit.\r\n\r\nAs an encouraging and supportive guide, I am here to walk alongside you on your wellness journey.\r\n\r\nWelcome to my holistic therapy practice, where your well-being is at the heart of everything I do. I’m dedicated to helping you achieve harmony across your physical, emotional, and spiritual realms. In the sanctuary of my space, you’ll find comfort and warmth—a place where you can truly feel at ease.\r\n\r\nMy expertise lies in the powerful combination of essential oils, the healing energy of Reiki, Essential Emotions Coaching, and the techniques of Neuro-Linguistic Programming. These dynamic tools empower my clients to reach their optimal state of health and vitality.\r\n\r\nMy personal journey with essential oils began in 2021 after a life-changing car accident. The oils became a vital part of my recovery, restoring my physical balance and enhancing my overall well-being. Through Reiki, I have navigated complex challenges in my relationships, discovering the transformative power of presence, balance, and the body’s innate ability to heal on all levels\r\n\r\nWhen you choose to work with me, you are embarking on a voyage of transformation. Your session with me will offer a sanctuary of relaxation, authenticity, and healing.\r\n\r\nI look forward to connecting with you and guiding you on this transformative journey toward a more vibrant, centered, and fulfilled life.', NULL, '11,106,107,108', '4,31,35,36', '[]', '19,20,21,22,23', 'America/Toronto', NULL, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-03-02 05:16:13', '2025-03-10 07:26:23', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_wednesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_thursday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_friday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"weekends_only_-_every_sat_&_sundays\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null}}', NULL),
