(38, 38, 'I’m a Massage Therapist, Somatic and Root Cause Coach, the Massage Therapist for your inward journey! I guide women who feel like they are hitting up against their edges, to relax into and trust their inner guidance; expand their capacity to live their lives authentically. I use a heart-centered approach and hold a safe space to guide you towards self-awareness, healing, curiosity and self-empowerment.', 'Integrative Bodywork', '[\"395\"]', '[\"7\",\"10\",\"20\",\"22\",\"23\",\"42\",\"43\",\"45\",\"54\"]', '{\"profile_image\":\"1740902288_1-1.png\"}', 'With over 24 years of experience as a massage therapist, I’ve helped thousands of people release physical tension and pain from their bodies.\r\nAfter years of doing bodywork, I felt a calling to explore new avenues of healing. I embarked on a journey into the realm of coaching, eager to support my clients on a deeper level. However, what I discovered along the way was truly transformative.\r\nI realized that the journey was as much for me as it was for my clients. It became an opportunity to reconnect with my own body and emotions, unveiling layers of self-discovery and personal growth. Through introspection, I uncovered patterns of prioritizing others\' needs above my own and having negative thoughts about myself, leading to a profound realization: I had been neglecting my own well-being in the process.\r\nMy Vision is guiding women on an inward journey of healing and authenticity to access the answers within, empowering their fullest expression through aligned decisions, awakening them to create the life they desire.', NULL, '2,10,11,13,19,166', '4,11,41,63,162,163,177,178,179', '[]', '1,2,3,4,72,73,74,75', 'America/New_York', '[\"Virtual offerings\"]', 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-03-02 05:16:14', '2025-03-20 00:28:46', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":\"15:00\",\"to\":\"19:00\"},\"every_wednesday\":