(43, 43, 'Heidi is a certified shamanic and Womb Awakening practitioner with a deep connection to the unseen realms. Her gentle, nurturing energy supports individuals on their journey of self-discovery and healing through ceremony. Drawing from her many years on the spiritual path and her training in core shamanism and Sacred Womb Awakening, Heidi creates sacred spaces for healing, transformation and the remembrance of one\'s own power.', 'Vital Resonance', '[\"116\"]', '[]', '{\"profile_image\":\"1740932620_IMG_7440-scaled.jpg\"}', 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nYTrIcn4rjg\r\nGrowing up in the pacific northwest I was always within close proximity to the natural world. From a young age my summers were spent on our family boat exploring the magical inlets and tidal pools of the Salish Sea. This close connection to nature and specifically the ocean was significant for me in moving through the challenges of my childhood and adolescent years. The sound of lapping waves against our boat, the call of seagulls flying overhead and the warm sand beneath my feet was the healing salve for my tender heart. I am deeply grateful for the continued support, wisdom and teachings of Mother Ocean.\r\nMy early 20\'s were spent working and travelling abroad in Australia, New Zealand, Europe and South East Asia. At 26 years old I returned from travelling and settled in Victoria, BC where I completed my bachelor\'s degree in social work at the University of Victoria. After 10 years working in a field that was not aligned with my soul, Spirit called me to fully step into my purpose work. The call to deepen into my personal healing, and open to my gifts as a healer was experienced through numerous nudges and synchronistic events that unfolded over many years.\r\nAfter spending over a decade and thousands of dollars trying to \"fix\" what was \"wrong\" with me, it wasn\'t until I became a mother that I experienced true healing. Becoming a mother brought with it the highest of highs and the lowest of lows. My most painful and powerful initiations have arisen throughout my journey of motherhood. The medicine that I offer to those that I work with and support is rooted in my many experiences of breaking (death), and then healing (rebirth) along this path. It has been through my ongoing practice of shamanic journeying and sacred womb work that I have been able to connect to my feminine wisdom, cultivate deep self love and truly trust in the power of surrendering.\r\nI hold respect and reverence for the medicine I carry, which is woven from my ancestors, my own life journey, my teachers in this realm and especially my teachers in the Spirit realm.', NULL, '1,5,7,11,12,16,18,69,95,123,157,161,166,207,208,209,210,211,212,214,226,228,229,230,231,232,233,236', '1,8,73,74,75,76,77,78,79,80,81,82,83', '[]', '[]', 'America/Los_Angeles', NULL, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-03-02 05:16:15', '2025-03-10 07:58:57', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_wednesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_thursday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_friday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"weekends_only_-_every_sat_&_sundays\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null}}', NULL),
(44, 44, 'Isabel Nantaba is a gifted soul like you and serves as a spiritual guide and conduit for energy healing and transformative practices to transcend generational wounds and trauma. With a deep reverence for the mystical world, she is dedicated to harnessing the power of wisdom to help women rediscover their sacred feminine and awaken the healer within. As both a loving mother and wife, Isabel embodies the essence of nurturing and harmony in all aspects of her life.', 'Isabel NantabaBusiness', '[\"115\",\"908\"]', '[\"6\",\"7\",\"23\",\"25\",\"27\",\"30\",\"45\",\"52\",\"54\",\"73\",\"74\",\"76\",\"77\"]', '{\"profile_image\":\"1740929164_Untitled-design-20.png\"}', 'Born and raised in Uganda, my journey with healing and empowerment began early. Spending holidays in my grandmother’s village, I watched her intuitively use plants and herbs from the garden to create remedies for various ailments. She would gather ingredients to make teas, juices, or herbal baths, sparking my lifelong passion for plants, nature, and natural healing.\r\n\r\nGrowing up, I also felt a deep connection to the stars, often gazing up at the night sky with an inner knowing that I wasn’t only bound to this earth; I sensed a belonging somewhere beyond. This connection was one of many spiritual realizations that shaped my path.\r\n\r\nAs a teenager, I was actively involved in church, leading youth workshops and engaging in spiritual activities. During a period of deep prayer, I experienced speaking in tongues—what is known today as light language—a powerful experience that marked the start of my spiritual journey.\r\n\r\nIn 2014, I explored Reiki, and in 2018, I attended yoga teacher training at an ashram in Val Morin, Quebec. Through dedicated practice, I experienced a powerful energy awakening, which led me to become a certified Usui and Angelic Reiki Master and trained in Energy Mastery. Embracing light language further expanded my spiritual practice, and since 2019, I’ve facilitated both private and group energy healing sessions.\r\n\r\nProfessionally, I pursued a master’s degree in International Cooperation and Development in Spain, working part-time with Solidaridad Internacional to facilitate community support workshops for immigrant women. This role allowed me to connect with people from diverse backgrounds, enriching my understanding of cultural and community resilience. Later, I worked with the United Nations Development Program at the Regional Headquarters for Latin America and the Caribbean in Panama, gaining insight into global development and cooperation.\r\n\r\nAfter moving to Canada, I coordinated a women\'s program with Women\'s Health in Women’s Hands, facilitating workshops on women\'s sexual health and well-being. This role reinforced my passion for women’s empowerment, which I now channel into my work helping women reconnect with their bodies and embrace their feminine energy.\r\n\r\nToday, as the founder of Elevating Herbs, I create herbal teas and tinctures to support physical, mental, and spiritual well-being. I integrate my professional experience, love of nature, and dedication to holistic healing to empower women in their journeys of self-discovery, healing, and embodiment.', NULL, '6,7,16,66,68,97,112,114,119,127,142,143,144,165', '6,8,10,27,28,44,54,57,73,78,80,81,136', '[]', '11,30,31,89', 'America/Toronto', '[\"Virtual offerings\",\"Flexible packages\",\"Payment plans\"]', 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-03-02 05:16:15', '2025-03-18 02:50:45', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_wednesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_thursday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_friday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"weekends_only_-_every_sat_&_sundays\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null}}', NULL),
(45, 45, 'I am a certified tarot reader and a Dating - Relationship coach. I provide spiritual guidance for all kinds of life problems using tarot & oracle cards. I teach women how to tap into their feminine energy to become their most magnetic self ever by shifting their mindset and counselling them on how to balance their masculine and feminine energies. Reach out to me if you need help getting unstuck from a toxic relationship, toxic twin flame dynamic or manifesting your soulmate.', 'Rare Intuition', '[\"372\"]', '[]', NULL, 'https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nYTrIcn4rjg', NULL, '63,64,65,66,67,68,69', '8,9,10,11,12,13', '[]', '13,14', 'America/Edmonton', NULL, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-03-02 05:16:15', '2025-03-10 08:00:48', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_wednesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_thursday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_friday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"weekends_only_-_every_sat_&_sundays\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null}}', NULL),
(46, 46, 'My journey has taught me to embrace every part of myself, transforming even the deepest pain into growth and healing. I weave this wisdom into my practice, offering Reiki, crystal healing, sound healing, and meditation to support others. Through one-on-one sessions, workshops, retreats, and immersive experiences, I hold a nurturing space for self-exploration and empowerment, meeting you exactly where you are on your path.', 'Soulful Connections', '[\"115\"]', '[\"7\",\"8\",\"11\",\"19\",\"25\",\"31\",\"33\",\"40\"]', '{\"profile_image\":\"1740929911_janine1111.jpg\",\"media_images\":[\"1742608419_sound healing1.jpg\"]}', NULL, NULL, '11,16,67,96,97,143,165,166', '2,4,8,11,12,22,54,60,110', '[\"1\",\"7\",\"9\"]', '32,71', 'America/Toronto', '[\"Virtual offerings\"]', 0, 0, 0, 'Your privacy is deeply respected. Any personal information shared during sessions or communication will be kept strictly confidential and used only to support your healing journey. The only exception is if there is a concern for your safety or the safety of others, in which case appropriate support may be sought.', 'By booking a session or experience, you acknowledge that you are honouring your own well-being, and understand that the offerings provided are meant to support your healing journey and personal growth. These sessions and experiences are a complement to your journey and are not a substitute for medical or psychological care.', '2025-03-02 05:16:15', '2025-03-22 02:00:47', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":\"17:00\",\"to\":\"21:30\"},\"every_wednesday\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":\"17:00\",\"to\":\"21:30\"},\"every_thursday\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":\"17:00\",\"to\":\"21:30\"},\"every_friday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"weekends_only_-_every_sat_&_sundays\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":\"11:00\",\"to\":\"16:00\"}}', 'If you need to cancel or reschedule, please le