(49, 49, 'I\'m a Regenerative Health Practitioner and an award-winning Holistic Nutritionist passionate about supporting others to their best health possible. My speciality is addressing root causes of autoimmune conditions and parasites. I\'ve used nutrition, detoxification protocols and various holistic health practices to reverse a Hashimoto’s and hypothyroidism diagnosis in my own body. I use nutrition, herbs, mindset, and cutting edge biohacks to work with clients.', 'Balance Life with Julie', '[\"923\"]', '[]', '{\"profile_image\":\"1740912261_Julie-Brar_Profile-Photo.jpeg\"}', 'https://www.youtube.com/@balancelifewithjulie\r\nI\'m a Regenerative Health Practitioner and an award-winning Holistic Nutritionist passionate about supporting others to better health using a whole food plant based diet. I also holds several yoga certifications and taught yoga prior to shifting into Regenerative Health.\r\n\r\nMy speciality is addressing root causes of autoimmune conditions, gut health and parasites. I\'ve used nutrition, detoxification protocols and various holistic health practices to reverse Hashimoto’s and hypothyroidism diagnosis in my own body. I use nutrition, herbs, mindset, EFT, movement and cutting edge bio hacks to help clients achieve their optimal health.\r\n\r\nI\'m also a published author in a collaborative book project, The Courage to Change, which hit the bestseller list on Amazon. In my spare time I loves to write, experiment with new recipes and ride my Harley. I love traveling with my fiancé and our 3 dogs.', NULL, '15,109,112,113,114,115,116,117,118,119,120,121,122,123,124,125,126,127,128,129,130,131,132', '40', '[]', '[]', 'America/Toronto', NULL, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-03-02 05:16:16', '2025-03-10 07:33:09', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_wednesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_thursday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"