(52, 52, 'Lauren has been reading tarot cards for 9 years, and works with them as a beautiful tool to champion the answers you already have inside yourself but can\'t always see. Her readings are compassionate and intuitively guided, as she meets you right where you are. Lauren is currently studying hypnotherapy at the International Institute of Hypnotherapy, and is excited to additionally be offering hypnotherapy services in 2025.', 'Lauren Welchner Tarot Readings', '[\"115\"]', '[]', '{\"profile_image\":\"1740909408_005A1767-scaled.jpg\"}', 'I have been reading tarot cards for 9 years, and work with them as a beautiful tool to champion the answers you already have inside yourself but can\'t always see. My readings are compassionate and intuitively guided, as I meet you right where you are.\r\n\r\nMy readings include tarot and oracle card interpretations, my own intuitive guidance, as well as an offering of my highest spiritual understanding of the issue you\'re facing. Whether you\'re feeling stuck, unsure what decision to make, unsure if a connection is good for you, or just needing some reassurance that you\'re heading in a direction that\'s aligned for you, it is my honour to work with you to find the clarity you need to move forward. It is my intention for each person to leave a reading with me feeling understood, empowered, lighter, and with more clarity.\r\n\r\nMy own spiritual practice, which is ever-evolving, includes meditation, yoga, plant medicine, hypnotherapy, and of course tarot readings.\r\n\r\nI am currently studying hypnotherapy at the International Institute of Hypnotherapy, and I am excited to additionally be offering hypnotherapy services in 2025.', NULL, '6,11,16,66,77,97,108,143,157,236,266', '14,15', '[]', '[]', 'America/Toronto', NULL, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-03-02 05:16:17', '2025-03-10 07:13:30', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},