(54, 54, 'Mel is a facilitator and wellness guide dedicated to supporting women in their menstrual cycle wellness and yoni steaming practices. With a deep respect for the wisdom of the body and the cyclical nature of life, she offers personalized yoni steaming consultations and in-person sessions, helping women reconnect with their womb space and honor their body’s natural rhythms. Through nurturing guidance, she provides the tools and resources to support healing, balance, and empowerment. Mel’s work is rooted in holistic care, honoring the sacred connection between body, mind, and spirit, with a focus on menstrual health and self-care practices', 'Sacred Coast', '[\"752\"]', '[\"4\",\"5\",\"6\",\"11\",\"13\",\"25\",\"40\",\"53\"]', '{\"profile_image\":\"1740913573_The-storis-1.png\",\"media_images\":[\"1742233967_020A5586.jpg\",\"1742233967_020A5608.jpg\"]}', 'As a passionate advocate for women\'s wellness, I work with girls and women to embrace their menstrual cycles as a sacred and transformative journey. By exploring the deep connections between our bodies, nature, and the rhythms of the earth and moon, I support individuals to tap into their innate wisdom and feminine power.\r\n\r\nThrough workshops, personalized sessions, and community gatherings, I create a nurturing space where we can celebrate our cycles, honor our emotions, and cultivate self-awareness. Together, we will discover how aligning with our natural rhythms can lead to profound healing and empowerment.', NULL, '3,4,5,7,11,13,16,65,67,106,123,132,142,143,144,157,161,162,190', '8,10,11,17,27,29,53,54,56,74,78,97,102', '[\"5\"]', '88', 'America/Vancouver', '[\"Virtual offerings\"]', 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-03-02 05:16:17', '2025-03-17 17:52:47', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":\"2025-04-01T10:00\",\"to\":\"2025-06-17T10:00\"},\"every_wednesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_thursda