(57, 57, 'Anna i. Azuis cena a Visual Creative Artist who infuses intention into every piece she creates. Through the synergy of colors, words, plants, and textures, she crafts art that is both meaningful and transformative. Her work is deeply rooted in energy, emotion, and the power of visualization, inviting others into a space of self-expression and inner exploration.\r\n\r\n\r\nAs the founder of AromArt Wellness, Anna curates immersive Creative Wellness Workshops that blend art with intentional Visual Meditation. Each month, she guides participants through themed creative sessions, helping them connect with their emotions and imagination. These workshops are designed to be more than just artistic exercises—they are experiences that promote relaxation, clarity, and self-discovery.\r\n\r\nAt the heart of her practice is Visual Meditation, a unique technique she has developed to teach others how to harness their mind’s eye. Through guided storytelling, breathwork, sound healing, essential oils, and affirmations, she helps individuals visualize their aspirations, release creative blocks, and step into a more aligned version of themselves. She believes that if we can see something in our minds, we have the power to bring it into reality.\r\n\r\nAnnaersonalized Visual Meditations, tailoring them to individual needs by exploring personal intentions, emotional blocks, and physical discomforts. She creates customized essential oil blends to support each meditation, ensuring a holistic and deeply personal experience.\r\n\r\nBeyond group workshops, she offers private 1:1 sessions, allowing clients to meditate, paint, or combine both for a deeply personal journey of creativity and self-reflection. She also hosts intimate home-based workshops, where small groups of up to six friends or couples can gather for a transformative and artistic experience in a familiar, comfortable setting.\r\n\r\nWith a passion for guiding others toward healing and creative freedom, Anna continues to merge art, mindfulness, and intention to inspire individuals to step into their most expressive and empowered selves.', NULL, '[\"115\"]', '[\"15\",\"16\",\"17\",\"18\",\"19\"]', '{\"profile_image\":\"1741646343_Untitled design (9).jpg\"}', NULL, NULL, '143,300,329,330,331,332,333', '8,9,10,11', '[]', '[]', 'America/Toronto', '[\"Virtual offerings\",\"Home visits\",\"Herbal Tea\\/beverages\"]', 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-03-02 05:16:17', '2025-03-12 02:01:10', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_wednesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_thursday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_friday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"weekends_only_-_every_sat_&_sundays\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null}}', NULL),
(58, 58, 'Raizelle Aspilla is a dedicated Sound Healer and Yoga Instructor who traveled to Pokhara, Nepal, in October 2023, where she completed her 200-hour yoga teacher training and earned her Level 1 & 2 sound healing certifications. With a background in Kinesiology and Health Science from York University, Raizelle blends her academic knowledge with holistic healing practices, helping clients achieve balance in their physical, emotional, mental, and spiritual well-being.', 'Auraligned Healing', '[\"956\"]', '[]', '{\"profile_image\":\"1740936293_IMG_0070.jpg\"}', 'https://www.instagram.com/reel/C_yvK67OcpB/?utm_source=ig_web_copy_link&igsh=MzRlODBiNWFlZA==\r\nMy journey into the world of healing began with my personal search for balance and clarity. I’m Raizelle Aspilla, a Sound Healer and Yoga Instructor, and for over a decade, I’ve immersed myself in practices that have transformed my life in profound ways. What started as a need to heal my own mind and body has grown into a passion for guiding others on their own paths toward healing and well-being.\r\n\r\nDuring 2022, I was seeking deeper meaning and alignment. I felt disconnected and overwhelmed by the pressures of life, but as I explored Sound Healing and Yoga, I experienced shifts I never thought possible. These practices grounded me, brought peace to my mind, and helped me release physical tension and emotional blockages I didn’t realize I was holding. I began to see how much energy and sound could shift my internal world, which sparked a deep desire to learn more about these ancient techniques.\r\n\r\nIn 2017, I earned my Bachelor of Arts in Kinesiology and Health Sciences, which gave me a solid foundation in understanding the human body and its functions. This academic knowledge, paired with the spiritual growth I experienced through yoga and sound healing, led me to fully embrace a holistic approach to wellness. My training in Hatha and Ashtanga yoga taught me how to combine physical movement with breath, creating a space for emotional release and inner peace. It was a way for me to move beyond the surface, diving deep into the mental and spiritual aspects of well-being.\r\n\r\nSound Healing became a natural extension of this journey. I traveled to Pokhara, Nepal, where I completed my Level 1 and 2 certifications in Sound Healing, using Tibetan singing bowls and other instruments to help restore balance to the mind and body. The vibrational energy from these instruments resonates at a cellular level, helping to release tension, calm the nervous system, and promote healing. I witnessed firsthand the transformative power of sound, both for myself and for those I’ve worked with.\r\n\r\nNow, through Auraligned Healing, I offer sound healing sessions and yoga instruction to others, combining my knowledge of the body, mind, and spirit to create a holistic healing experience. I believe that healing is not a one-size-fits-all process—each person’s journey is unique. My goal is to provide a safe, supportive environment where you can explore your own healing process, whether that’s through a sound bath, a personalized sound healing session, or a yoga practice tailored to your needs.\r\n\r\nI am deeply committed to helping others find balance, peace, and clarity. Just as these practices have helped me, I’m passionate about sharing this knowledge so others can connect with their own inner healing. Whether you’re new to sound healing and yoga or a seasoned practitioner, I’m here to walk with you on your journey to well-being.', NULL, '4,13,17,21,96,109,166,263,281,282,286', '2,7,104,105,106,109,110,111,112,114,115', '[]', '12,30', 'America/Toronto', '[\"Bathrooms\",\"Herbal Tea\\/beverages\",\"Waiting area\"]', 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-03-02 05:16:18', '2025-03-17 03:59:44', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_wednesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_thursd