(64, 64, 'Shanice helps women prioritize themselves through holistic beauty and wellness services. By blending beauty treatments, spiritual healing, and self-care products, she empowers women to align their body, mind, and spirit. With a background in health studies and a passion for healing, Shanice offers women a safe space to reconnect with themselves and embrace their personal power.', 'Temple Body & Beauty', '[\"115\"]', '[]', '{\"profile_image\":\"1740910055_SHANICE_2-scaled.jpg\"}', 'Shanice is the founder of Temple Body & Beauty, a holistic wellness brand designed to nurture women’s physical, spiritual, and emotional well-being. With a degree in health studies and years of experience working with women overcoming trauma, Shanice recognized the need for a supportive, inclusive space where women could focus on self-care and holistic healing.\r\n\r\nTemple Body & Beauty offers a blend of beauty services, spiritual healing, and self-care products, allowing women to prioritize their well-being in a way that suits their unique needs. Shanice’s services include Reiki healing, spiritual coaching, and beauty treatments such as eyelash and brow services, all with the aim of helping women restore balance in their lives. Her approach is deeply rooted in the belief that true wellness comes from caring for the whole person—mind, body, and spirit.\r\n\r\nShanice is passionate about creating a nurturing environment where women from all walks of life can connect with their inner strength, reclaim their personal power, and experience transformational healing. She believes that when women take the time to care for themselves, they become better equipped to handle the challenges of daily life and make a positive impact on their communities.\r\n\r\nHer work extends beyond beauty treatments. Shanice also provides workshops focused on empowerment, self-discovery, and spiritual growth, helping women reconnect with themselves in a supportive community setting. She is dedicated to creating an inclusive space where women can explore their wellness journey and find the tools they need to thrive.\r\n\r\nShanice’s commitment to holistic wellness is not just about physical beauty—it’s about fostering self-love, self-awareness, and personal growth. Through Temple Body & Beauty, she is on a mission to empower women to live healthier, happier, and more fulfilling lives.', NULL, '1,2,4,7,11,17,63,67,95,96,97,157,165,300,306,317', '4,15,16,17,22,27,28,29,30', '[]', '1,2,18', 'America/Toronto', NULL, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-03-02 05:16:19', '2025-03-10 07:19:01', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_wednesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_thursday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_friday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"weekends_only_-_every_sat_&_sundays\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null}}', NULL),
