(68, 68, 'Hi, I’m Tiana! I help women in their 40s lose weight and get into the best shape of their life. I am the founder and creator of the Fit over 40 Blueprint where I teach women how to unlock their anti inflammation switch through mindset, whole food nutrition and movement. AKA no pills, injections or dieting. My goal is to help you tap into your magic and empower you to make the decisions that align to your highest self to create the life and body you desire.', 'Tiana Pollari Wellness Coaching', '[\"115\"]', '[]', '{\"profile_image\":\"1740936786_Desired-Media-Tiana-72-scaled.jpg\"}', 'When we work together, I make it easy for you to make decisions from a position of power without overthinking so that you can step into the most powerful version of yourself and love what you see in the mirror. We’ll get to the core of your challenges so that you can have the breakthroughs you’ve been looking for and more importantly how to love yourself through the process.', NULL, '7,11,67,97,108,144,157,242,300', '42,49', '[]', '42,66,67', 'America/Toronto', NULL, 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-03-02 05:16:20', '2025-03-10 08:10:25', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_wednesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_thursday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_friday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"weekends_only_-_every_sat_&_sundays\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null}}', NULL);
