(71, 71, 'I’m a Certified Aromatherapist with the Canadian Federation of Aromatherapy, Reiki Master, tarot reader and practicing chaos witch. I specialize in using essential oils, along with tarot, reiki and crystals to help anyone who feels like they no longer have control over aspects of their lives, may be spiritually lost or just wants to start living a more authentic life. I use essential oils with their clinical as well as metaphysical properties to treat a variety of physical and emotional ailments with aromatherapy and reiki.', 'Enchanted Forest Aromatherapy and Divination', '[\"1019\"]', '[\"7\",\"12\",\"17\",\"59\",\"61\",\"62\"]', '{\"profile_image\":\"1740937399_mvw_in_park-scaled.jpg\"}', 'I’m a recovering corporate newspaper chick who has finally found what she wants to do with her life. I’ve been a practicing witch for most of my life and started reading tarot when I was thirteen. I love being able to combine everything that inspires me into one and use it to help other people find their passion for life. As someone who found it difficult to found my place in this world until I was in my forties, I feel especially draw to help people find what really nourishes their soul. Using essential oils, tarot, reiki and crystals in my everyday life keeps me grounded and focused and I love to share that practice with anyone struggling in any aspect of their lives.', NULL, '5,6,7,8,10,11,12,17,19,66,96,97,109,119,123,130,165,229,236,263,281,282,286,302,303,304,306,308,309', '4,14,118,168', '[\"1\",\"7\",\"11\"]', '11,68', 'America/Toronto', '[\"Virtual offerings\"]', 0, 0, 0, NULL, NULL, '2025-03-02 05:16:20', '2025-03-17 16:18:16', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_tuesday\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_wednesday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_thursday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_friday\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"weekends_only_-_e