(79, 79, 'As an artist and spiritual seeker, Kingsley has cultivated a unique approach to BreathPlay™ that blends music, mindfulness, and guided breathing techniques. Through years of personal practice and guiding others, Kingsley has created a safe and transformative space for you to explore your inner world and step into alignment with your purpose.\r\n\r\nBreathPlay™ is a revolutionary concept created by Kingsley, redefining the narrative of breathwork and reclaiming it from the ways Western society has often oversimplified and commodified this ancient practice. BreathPlay™ is an immersive art form that explores how intentional breathing can profoundly impact your brain, body, and spirit on physical, emotional, and spiritual levels. Drawing on years of study and practice, Kingsley has crafted a transformative experience that blends mindfulness, education, music integration, affirmations, visualization, manifestation, and more into a seamless and powerful journey of self-discovery and empowerment.\r\n\r\nRemember, your breath isn’t a practice—it’s a playground. Explore it, expand with it, and let it guide you into deeper creativity, presence, and so much more.', NULL, '[]', '[\"11\",\"15\",\"24\",\"25\",\"79\"]', '{\"media_images\":[],\"profile_image\":\"1742402210_HIRA ITEMS.png\"}', NULL, NULL, '7,11,16,17,22,63,67,157,322', '10,11,95,101,175,176', '[]', '93', 'America/Los_Angeles', '[\"Virtual offerings\",\"Home visits\",\"Payment plans\"]', 0, 0, 0, 'Kings\' Kitchen Media (\"we,\" \"our,\" or \"us\") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy describes how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you engage with our BreathPlay™ services through our website www.kingskitchenmedia.com.\r\n\r\n1. Information We Collect\r\nWe may collect the following types of personal information:\r\nPersonal Identifiers: Name, email address, phone number, and payment details when you book a BreathPlay™ session.\r\nHealth Information: Voluntary disclosures related to your well-being to tailor the BreathPlay™ experience to your needs.\r\nUsage Data: Information about your interactions with our website, including IP address, browser type, and access times.\r\n\r\n2. How We Use Your Information\r\nProvide and personalize your BreathPlay™ sessions.\r\nProcess payments securely through Stripe. Improve our website and services.\r\nSend important communications about bookings, updates, and promotions (you can opt out anytime).\r\n\r\n3. How We Share Your Information\r\nWe do not sell or rent your personal data. However, we may share your information with:\r\nService Providers: Third-party platforms (such as Stripe for payment processing) that assist in delivering our services.\r\nLegal Compliance: If required by law or to protect our rights, safety, and property.\r\n\r\n4. Data Security\r\nWe implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal data. However, no online platform is 100% secure, and we encourage you to use strong passwords and protect your personal information.\r\n\r\n5. Your Rights & Choices\r\nYou have the right to: Access, update, or request deletion of your personal information. Opt out of promotional emails by clicking the “unsubscribe” link.\r\n\r\n6. Changes to This Privacy Policy\r\nWe may update this Privacy Policy as needed. Any changes will be posted on our website with the updated effective date.\r\n\r\n7. Contact Us\r\nFor any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:\r\nkingsley@kingskitchenmedia.com', 'By booking a BreathPlay™ session through the HIRA Collective , you agree to the following terms:\r\n\r\n1. Services & Booking\r\nBreathPlay™ sessions are for wellness, relaxation, and self-discovery. They are not a substitute for medical or psychological treatment.\r\nAll bookings must be made in advance and are subject to availability.\r\n\r\n2. Payments & Cancellations\r\nPayment is required at the time of booking via Stripe.\r\nCancellations made at least 24 hours in advance may be rescheduled. No refunds are provided for missed or late-canceled sessions.\r\n\r\n3. Liability Disclaimer\r\nBy participating in BreathPlay™, you acknowledge that you are responsible for your own well-being and will inform the facilitator of any medical conditions. Kings\' Kitchen Media is not liable for any physical, mental, or emotional effects that may arise from your participation.\r\n\r\n4. Privacy & Confidentiality\r\nYour personal information is handled according to our Privacy Policy. All shared experiences during sessions remain confidential.\r\n\r\n5. Changes to Terms\r\nWe reserve the right to update these Terms & Conditions at any time. Continued use of our services constitutes acceptance of any changes.', NULL, '2025-03-19 16:36:50', NULL, '{\"every_day\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null},\"every_monday\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":\"13:00\",\"to\":\"18:00\"},\"every_tuesday\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":\"13:00\",\"to\":\"18:00\"},\"every_wednesday\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":\"13:00\",\"to\":\"18:00\"},\"every_thursday\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":\"13:00\",\"to\":\"18:00\"},\"every_friday\":{\"enabled\":\"1\",\"from\":\"13:00\",\"to\":\"18:00\"},\"weekends_only_-_every_sat_&_sundays\":{\"from\":null,\"to\":null}}', 'Cancellations made at least 24 hours in advance may be rescheduled. No refunds are provided for missed or late-canceled sessions. \r\nPlease contact kingsley@kingkitchenmedia.com'),
